elling elements.\n\nSo, the main aspects to focus on are: following the instruction, using high-end techniques, creative plating, innovative pairings, storytelling, texture variety, ingredient quality, and service presentation. Let me check if these are binary and if they can be evaluated as yes/no.\n\n1. **Instruction Following**: Does the response directly address the task of reimagining street foods in a high-end setting? Yes/No.\n2. **High-End Techniques**: Use of molecular gastronomy, spherification, emulsification, etc. Yes/No.\n3. **Creative Plating**: Unique and artistic presentation. Yes/No.\n4. **Innovative Pairings**: Creative food and drink pairings. Yes/No.\n5. **Storytelling**: Incorporates local stories or cultural context. Yes/No.\n6. **Texture Variety**: Contrasts like crispy, chewy, creamy. Yes/No.\n7. **Ingredient Quality**: Use of premium or local ingredients. Yes/No.\n8. **Service Presentation**: Attention to service details like tableside preparation. Yes/No.\n\nI need to make sure each criterion is specific and binary. The reference and samples all emphasize these points, so these criteria should cover the essential aspects. Now, I'll structure them into JSON as specified.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 한국 길거리 음식을 고급 식당에서 제공할 수 있는 창의적인 방법을 직접 제안합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"molecular_gastronomy\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 클리어 브로스, 에스푸마, 스펀지 등 분자 요리 기법을 활용해 재료를 재해석합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"plating_artistry\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 플레이팅에서 지역적 소재(백자, 온돌)와 현대적 디자인을 결합해 미학을 강조합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"innovative_pairing\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 음료(막걸리, 와인)와 메뉴 간 창의적인 페어링 전략을 제안합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"cultural_storytelling\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 지역성(부산 어묵, 전주 비빔)과 노점의 역사적 맥락을 스토리텔링으로 담습니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"texture_contrast\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 바삭-촉촉-크리미 등 다층적인 식감을 기술적으로 구현합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"ingredient_quality\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 제철 해산물, 토종 닭고기, 숙성 장을 활용해 재료의 고급화를 강조합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"service_presentation\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 테이블사이드 마무리(소스 붓기, 스모크)와 서비스 연출을 구체적으로 제안합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
