alism, adherence to safety, time management, and user engagement. Let me break these down.\n\n1. **Instruction Following**: Does the response follow the instruction to simulate a bus ride to school? The reference response does this, and the samples are interactive simulations. So, this is essential.\n\n2. **Scenario Setup**: The response should set up the scenario with details like time, weather, and items. The samples have specific settings, so this is important.\n\n3. **Interactivity**: The samples are interactive with choices, so the response should include elements that allow user interaction.\n\n4. **Problem-Solving**: The reference response mentions possible issues and solutions, so the rubric should check if the response addresses potential problems.\n\n5. **Realism**: The samples have realistic details like weather, time, and items. The rubric should ensure the response is realistic.\n\n6. **Safety Adherence**: The reference mentions masks and social distancing, so checking if safety measures are included is important.\n\n7. **Time Management**: The samples have time constraints, so the response should handle time-related aspects.\n\n8. **User Engagement**: The samples are engaging with choices, so the response should encourage user participation.\n\nNow, I need to make sure each criterion is binary (YES/NO) and specific. Let me check if these are all prompt-specific and not generic. Yes, each criterion relates directly to the simulation aspect of the prompt. The reference and samples all have these elements, so the criteria should be applicable.\n\nI need to assign each a weight and importance. The first two (instruction following and scenario setup) are essential, so they get higher weights. The others are important but maybe lower. The polarity is positive for all since they are about meeting the requirements.\n\nNow, translating these into the JSON structure. Each criterion has an ID, axis, importance, weight, polarity, text in Korean, and self_contained. The text should be specific, like \"응답은 학교를 가는 상황에서 버스를 타는 시뮬레이션을 명확히 수행한다\" for instruction following.\n\nI need to ensure that each criterion is distinct and covers different aspects. Let me list them again:\n\n1. Instruction Following\n2. Scenario Setup\n3. Interactivity\n4. Problem-Solving\n5. Realism\n6. Safety Adherence\n7. Time Management\n8. User Engagement\n\nYes, these are all different and specific. Now, I'll structure them into the JSON format as specified.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 학교를 가는 상황에서 버스를 타는 시뮬레이션을 명확히 수행한다\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"scenario_setup\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 시간, 날씨, 소지품 등 시뮬레이션 상황을 구체적으로 설정한다\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"interactivity\",\n      \"importance\": \"important\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 사용자 선택에 따라 결과가 달라지는 상호작용 요소를 포함한다\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"problem_solving\",\n      \"importance\": \"important\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 시뮬레이션 중 발생할 수 있는 문제점과 대처 방안을 제시한다\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"realism\",\n      \"importance\": \"important\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 현실적인 시간, 환경, 행동 요소를 구체적으로 묘사한다\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"safety_adherence\",\n      \"importance\": \"important\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 마스크 착용, 사회적 거리두기 등 안전 수칙을 포함한다\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"time_management\",\n      \"importance\": \"important\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 시간 제약 조건(예: 지각 방지)을 명확히 반영한다\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"user_engagement\",\n      \"importance\": \"important\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 사용자 선택에 따라 결과가 달라지는 참여 유도 요소를 포함한다\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
