platform competition, labor issues, regulatory changes, environmental impacts, and cultural shifts. \n\nEach criterion needs to be specific to the prompt and binary (yes/no). They should be based on the reference, not the samples. Let me think of 8 distinct areas. \n\n1. **Instruction Following**: Does the response directly address the impact of social distancing on food delivery and takeout culture? The reference does this, so this is essential.\n\n2. **Data and Statistics**: Does the response include quantitative data or specific examples? The reference uses numbers and examples, so this is important.\n\n3. **Digital Transformation**: Does it mention how digital tools (apps, online ordering) were used? The reference discusses this, so this is a key point.\n\n4. **Operational Changes in Restaurants**: Does it cover how restaurants adapted their operations? The reference does this, so this is another criterion.\n\n5. **Labor and Logistics**: Does it address changes in the delivery workforce and logistics? The reference mentions rider issues and logistics changes.\n\n6. **Regulatory and Policy Changes**: Does it discuss policy responses or regulations? The reference talks about policy changes, so this is a criterion.\n\n7. **Environmental Impact**: Does it mention environmental effects like waste from packaging? The reference includes this.\n\n8. **Cultural Shifts**: Does it discuss changes in consumer behavior or cultural norms? The reference covers this, like the shift to takeout and delivery.\n\nI need to make sure each criterion is specific, binary, and not generic. Also, avoid using terms from the samples. Let me structure each with the required fields.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 사회적 거리 두기의 직접적인 영향을 분석하고, 음식 배달 및 테이크아웃 문화의 변화를 명확히 설명합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"data_inclusion\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 수치적 통계(예: 거래액, 주문량, 수수료)나 구체적인 사례(예: 플랫폼 경쟁, 포장재 변화)를 포함하여 실증적 근거를 제시합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"digital_transformation\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 배달앱, 온라인 주문 시스템, 디지털 마케팅 등 디지털 도구의 역할을 구체적으로 설명합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"operational_changes\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 식당의 메뉴 재설계, 포장재 개선, 배달 전용 주방 등 운영 방식의 변화를 구체적으로 다룹니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"labor_logistics\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 배달 라이더의 수요 증가, 안전 문제, 물류 효율성 개선 등 노동 및 물류 생태계 변화를 분석합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"regulatory_impact\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 정책 변화(예: 수수료 규제, 환경 규제)와 그에 따른 산업 영향을 명확히 설명합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"environmental_impact\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 일회용 포장재 증가, 친환경 포장 전환 시도 등 환경적 영향을 구체적으로 분석합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"cultural_shifts\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 소비자 행동 변화(예: 비대면 선호, 테이크아웃 문화 확산)와 문화적 정착을 명확히 설명합니다.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
