ry connotation. The reference also notes that the nickname is a playful internet meme, not an official name.\n\nNow, looking at the sample responses, they all agree on the phonetic similarity and the origin as a meme. Some mention the derogatory aspect, while others note that it's a playful term. They also mention that it's not an official name and that the term has a slight negative connotation.\n\nSo, the key points to include in the criteria are:\n\n1. Whether the response correctly identifies the origin of the nickname as a phonetic similarity between \"Gemini\" and \"Jamin-i.\"\n2. Whether the response explains that \"Jamin-i\" is a Korean internet slang term for a childish or naive person.\n3. Whether the response clarifies that the nickname is not an official name.\n4. Whether the response mentions the slight derogatory connotation of the term.\n5. Whether the response notes that the nickname is a playful internet meme.\n6. Whether the response explains the context in which the nickname is used (e.g., in online communities).\n7. Whether the response differentiates between the official name and the nickname.\n8. Whether the response acknowledges that the nickname is not meant to be taken literally or as an official title.\n\nEach of these points should be a separate criterion. I need to make sure they are binary and specific. Let me check if these are all covered in the reference and samples. Yes, each of these points is addressed in the reference and the samples. Now, I need to phrase each criterion in Korean, ensuring they are clear and specific. Also, the criteria should be in the JSON format as specified.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 '잼민이'라는 별명의 출처를 정확히 설명한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 '잼민이'가 한국 인터넷 슬랭인 '재민이'에서 유래했다는 점을 명시한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 '잼민이'라는 별명이 공식 명칭이 아니라는 점을 설명한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 '잼민이'의 약간의 비하적 뉘앙스를 언급한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 '발음 유사성'이 별명의 출처였다는 점을 강조한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 '인터넷 밈' 또는 '은어'로 사용된다는 점을 설명한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 '공식 명칭과 별명의 구분'을 명확히 한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 별명이 '실제 모델의 특성'과 무관하다는 점을 언급한다.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
