 like economic effects, social impacts, cultural aspects, spatial planning, environmental effects, governance, and more.\n\nSo, the criteria should be based on these aspects. Let me think of 8 specific points. The first one is instruction following, which is essential. The reference response clearly follows the instruction, so that's a YES. Next, maybe the depth of analysis on economic impacts. The reference response discusses economic effects in detail, so that's a YES. Then, the inclusion of social impacts, which the reference does. Another could be the coverage of cultural aspects, which is present. Spatial planning is another point, as the reference talks about spatial distribution. Environmental considerations are covered. Governance structures are mentioned. Lastly, the balance between preservation and tourism. The reference addresses both, so that's a YES.\n\nWait, I need to make sure each criterion is specific and binary. Let me list them again:\n\n1. Instruction Following: Does the response strictly follow the user's request to compare the two places and analyze the impacts on tourism and the community?\n2. Economic Impact Analysis: Does the response thoroughly discuss the economic effects of cultural preservation?\n3. Social Impact Analysis: Does the response cover the social effects, like community cohesion and cultural identity?\n4. Cultural Aspect Coverage: Does the response include detailed cultural elements and their preservation?\n5. Spatial Planning: Does the response address the spatial distribution and planning related to the sites?\n6. Environmental Considerations: Does the response mention environmental impacts and sustainability?\n7. Governance Structures: Does the response discuss the governance and management frameworks?\n8. Balance Between Preservation and Tourism: Does the response strike a balance between preserving culture and promoting tourism?\n\nEach of these should be checked against the reference and sample responses. The reference response does cover all these points, so they would all be YES. The samples also elaborate on these aspects, so the criteria should be binary. Now, I need to structure this into the JSON format as specified, ensuring each criterion has the correct ID, axis, importance, weight, and text in Korean.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 전주 한옥마을과 경주 역사유적지를 비교하며 전통문화 보존이 관광과 지역사회에 미치는 영향을 구체적으로 분석하는 것이 요구된 요청을 완전히 따르고 있습니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"economic_impact_analysis\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 관광 수익, 지역경제 활성화, 일자리 창출 등 경제적 영향을 구조적으로 분석하고, 전주와 경주의 차이를 명확히 설명합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"social_impact_analysis\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 지역사회 정체성 강화, 세대 간 문화 전승, 주민-관광객 갈등 등 사회적 영향을 다각도로 논의하고 있습니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"cultural_aspect_coverage\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 전통 음식, 공예, 의례 등 무형유산의 보존과 현대적 재해석을 체계적으로 다루고 있습니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"spatial_planning\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 한옥마을의 골목형 공간과 유적지의 광역 분산 구조, 공간적 보존 방식을 구체적으로 비교 분석하고 있습니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"environmental_considerations\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 환경적 영향(생태계 보전, 교통 혼잡, 유적 훼손 방지)을 수용력 관리와 지속가능한 관광 전략에 연결해 논의하고 있습니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"governance_structures\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 주민 참여, 규제 기준, 공공-민간 협력 등 거버넌스 구조를 전주와 경주의 차이에 따라 구체적으로 분석하고 있습니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"balance_preservation_tourism\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 보존과 관광의 균형을 유지하기 위한 정책 제안(예: 수용력 관리, 상생 임대료, 체류형 콘텐츠)을 구조적으로 제시하고 있습니다.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
