lowing the instruction, using high-quality ingredients, creative plating, innovative techniques, storytelling, seasonal elements, beverage pairings, and service presentation. Each of these can be a criterion. But they need to be binary (yes/no) and specific to the prompt.\n\nLet me list possible criteria:\n\n1. Instruction Following: Does the response directly address the task of creative methods for high-end restaurants?\n2. Material Upgrades: Does it suggest using premium ingredients or high-end substitutes?\n3. Creative Plating: Does it describe innovative ways to present the food?\n4. Innovative Techniques: Does it use advanced cooking methods like sous-vide, foams, etc.?\n5. Storytelling: Does it include historical or cultural context for the dishes?\n6. Seasonal Elements: Does it mention using seasonal or local ingredients?\n7. Beverage Pairings: Does it suggest appropriate wine or drink pairings?\n8. Service Presentation: Does it describe unique service methods or presentations?\n\nNow, I need to ensure these are binary and specific. For example, \"Creative Plating\" would be yes if the response includes detailed, artistic plating ideas. \"Innovative Techniques\" would be yes if it uses techniques like foams, gels, etc.\n\nI should check if these criteria are not too vague. The reference and samples do mention specific techniques and elements, so these criteria should be valid. Each criterion should be checked against the response to see if it meets the requirement.\n\nI think these 8 criteria cover the key aspects from the reference and samples. Now, I'll structure them into JSON format as specified.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 '고급 식당에서 길거리 음식 제공 방법'을 명확히 제안합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"material_upgrades\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"재료를 고급 재료(예: 수제 떡, 신선 해산물)로 대체하는 아이디어가 포함됩니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"creative_plating\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"음식의 플레이팅 방식이 창의적이고 예술적인 디자인(예: 디저트 플레이트, 미니어처)으로 제안됩니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"innovative_techniques\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"저온 조리, 클리어 컨소메, 퓨레/젤/폼 등 고급 기술이 활용된 메뉴 아이디어가 포함됩니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"storytelling\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"메뉴에 역사적/문화적 배경 설명(예: 분식의 역사, 특정 음식의 유래)이 포함됩니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"seasonal_elements\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.1,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"계절별 재료 사용(예: 봄(달래), 여름(참외))가 제안된 메뉴가 포함됩니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"beverage_pairing\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.1,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"음료와의 조합(예: 브뤼, 차, 와인)이 메뉴 아이디어와 연계되어 제안됩니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"service_presentation\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.1,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"테이블사이드 연출(예: 국물 붓기, 소스 마무리) 또는 서비스 방식(예: 카트 서비스)이 포함됩니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
{"prompt_id": "prompt_c0a3d66000a0", "pair_id": "pair_2368dd076a7b", "method": "rrd_pairwise_reference", "generator_family": "qwen_small", "generator_model": "Qwen/Qwen3-4B-FP8", "criteria": [{"id": "F1", "axis": "instruction_following", "importance": "essential", "weight": 0.2941176470588235, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 사용자 요청을 직접적이고 빠짐없이 수행한다. [smoke:e94e43]", "self_contained": true}, {"id": "F2", "axis": "correctness", "importance": "essential", "weight": 0.2941176470588235, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 사실 오류와 근거 없는 단정을 피하고 정확한 내용을 제공한다. [smoke:96829b]", "self_contained": true}, {"id": "F3", "axis": "completeness", "importance": "important", "weight": 0.20588235294117643, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 핵심 요소를 누락하지 않고 필요한 설명을 포함한다. [smoke:e88823]", "self_contained": true}, {"id": "F4", "axis": "korean_naturalness", "importance": "important", "weight": 0.20588235294117643, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 자연스럽고 읽기 쉬운 한국어 문장을 사용한다. [smoke:5eff6f]", "self_contained": true}], "rar_items": [], "generation_metadata": {"fallback_used": "rrd_static_fallback", "errors": ["'\"satisfied\"'"], "auxiliary_sample_ids": ["sample_01", "sample_02", "sample_03", "sample_04", "sample_05", "sample_06", "sample_07", "sample_08"], "reference_guidance_used": true, "raw_output": "<think>\nOkay, I need to create 8 criteria for evaluating the responses to the user's request about creating an Euclidean-class SCP object related to \"company employee's dismissal\" with a humorous twist. The criteria should be specific to the prompt and binary (YES/NO). Let me start by understanding the reference response and the sample responses.\n\nThe reference response includes detailed sections like Object Class, Special Containment Procedures, Description, and a humorous backstory. The samples also have similar structures with specific details on containment, description, and humorous elements.\n\nFirst, I need to identify the key aspects that the user's request emphasizes. The main points are: creating an SCP object related to \"company employee's dismissal,\" including creative details on overview, features, isolation procedures, and a humorous twist in the backstory.\n\nLooking at the reference and samples, common elements are:\n1. Object classification (Euclidean)\n2. Special containment procedures (specific to the object)\n3. Description of the object's properties and effects\n4. Humorous or ironic twist in the backstory\n5. Detailed isolation procedures\n6. Specific examples of the object's effects on individuals\n7. Backstory that explains the origin and includes humor\n8. Compliance with the prompt's requirements (e.g., creative, detailed, humorous)\n\nNow, I need to translate these into 8 binary criteria. Each criterion should be specific and check if the response meets that aspect.\n\n1. **Instruction Following**: Does the response strictly follow the user's instruction to create an SCP object with specific features?\n2. **Object Classification**: Is the object correctly classified as Euclidean?\n3. **Special Containment Procedures**: Are the procedures detailed and specific to the object?\n4. **Description of Object**: Does the response provide a clear and detailed description of the object's properties and effects?\n5. **Humorous Twist**: Does the backstory include a humorous or ironic twist?\n6. **Isolation Procedures**: Are the isolation procedures detailed and appropriate for the object's nature?\n7. **Backstory Explanation**: Does the response include a plausible backstory that explains the object's origin?\n8. **Creativity and Detail**: Does the response demonstrate creativity and thorough detail in describing the object?\n\nI need to ensure each criterion is specific to the prompt and can be evaluated as a yes/no. Also, avoid generic advice and focus on the specific aspects of the SCP creation.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 '회사원의 퇴근'과 관련된 특징, 격리 절차, 백스토리의 유머러스한 반전을 포함한 SCP 재단 보고서 형식을 정확히 따르고 있다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"object_classification\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 객체를 유클리드(Euclid) 등급으로 명시하고, 해당 등급의 특성(일반적인 현실 왜곡, 비폭력적 격리)을 반영하고 있다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"special_procedures\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 객체의 격리 절차를 구체적으로 설명하고, 격리 환경, 접근 제한, 비상 대응 등 실질적인 조치를 포함하고 있다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"object_description\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 객체의 작동 메커니즘(예: 퇴근 시도 시 생성되는 장애물, 공간 재배치)을 명확히 설명하고, 비정상적 현상의 예시를 포함하고 있다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"humorous_twist\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 백스토리에서 객체의 기원이나 작동 원리에 대한 유머러스한 반전(예: 회사 내부의 '야근 캠페인'이 문제의 원인)을 포함하고 있다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"backstory_explanation\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 객체의 기원을 명확히 설명하고, 사회적/기술적 배경(예: AI 시스템의 이상 현상, 회사 문화)을 통해 객체의 작동 원리를 도출하고 있다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"creative_detail\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 객체의 작동 메커니즘, 격리 절차, 백스토리 등에 대한 창의적인 상상력과 세부적인 설명을 보여주고 있다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"risk_management\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 객체의 위험성을 평가하고, 격리 절차에서의 안전 조치(예: 비상 시스템, 인지 차단 장치)를 명확히 포함하고 있다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
