imilar points: language barriers, education, employment, health, legal issues, community integration, digital access, and data-based management. Each sample response includes detailed policies and programs.\n\nNow, I need to identify 8 specific criteria that can be used to judge the quality of responses. Each criterion should be a binary yes/no check. Let's brainstorm:\n\n1. **Instruction Following**: Does the response address both the challenges and proposed policies as per the prompt?\n2. **Comprehensive Coverage**: Does it cover all key areas like language, education, employment, etc.?\n3. **Concrete Policies**: Are the policies specific and actionable?\n4. **Stakeholder Involvement**: Does it mention collaboration between government and local communities?\n5. **Data-Driven Approach**: Does it include data collection or performance metrics?\n6. **Cultural Sensitivity**: Does it address cultural aspects and avoid stereotypes?\n7. **Feasibility**: Are the proposed policies realistic and implementable?\n8. **Inclusivity**: Does it ensure that all groups, including vulnerable populations, are included?\n\nWait, the user's reference response mentions a unified roadmap and stakeholder roles. The samples also include specific programs like language courses, community centers, etc. So, maybe the criteria should be more aligned with the structure of the response.\n\nLet me adjust:\n\n1. **Instruction Following**: Does the response address both challenges and policy proposals?\n2. **Comprehensive Coverage**: Does it cover all key areas (language, education, employment, etc.)?\n3. **Specific Policies**: Are the policies detailed and actionable?\n4. **Stakeholder Collaboration**: Does it involve government and local community?\n5. **Data and Metrics**: Does it include data collection or performance indicators?\n6. **Cultural Sensitivity**: Does it address cultural aspects and avoid stereotypes?\n7. **Feasibility**: Are the policies realistic and implementable?\n8. **Inclusivity**: Does it ensure all groups are included?\n\nYes, these seem to cover the necessary aspects. Now, I need to translate these into Korean, make sure they are binary, and ensure they are specific to the prompt. Also, check that they are not generic. The reference response and samples all include these elements, so the criteria should be based on that.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 다문화 가정의 사회 통합 과정에서의 주요 어려움과 정부·지역사회 협력 정책을 모두 포함하고 있는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"comprehensive_coverage\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 언어 장벽, 교육 격차, 고용 문제, 건강 접근성, 사회적 차별 등 다문화 가정의 핵심 문제를 모두 다루고 있는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"specific_policies\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 구체적인 정책 제안(예: 언어 교육 프로그램, 지역사회 통합센터)을 포함하고 있는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"stakeholder_involvement\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 정부와 지역사회가 협력하여 정책을 실행할 수 있는 구조(예: 통합 컨트롤타워, 지역 멘토링)를 제안하고 있는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"data_and_metrics\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 성과 지표(예: 언어 능력 향상률, 취업률)나 데이터 기반 관리 방안을 제시하고 있는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"cultural_sensitivity\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 문화적 민감성(예: 이중언어 지원, 다문화 리더 양성)을 고려하고 있는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"feasibility\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 현실적인 실행 가능성(예: 농산어촌 이동 서비스, 소규모 창업 지원)을 포함하고 있는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"inclusivity\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 취약 계층(예: 여성 이주자, 2세)과 지역별 차이를 고려해 포괄적 접근을 제안하고 있는가?\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
