{"prompt_id": "prompt_b4eac90eab4a", "pair_id": "pair_274258fe8172", "method": "rrd_pairwise_reference", "generator_family": "qwen_small", "generator_model": "Qwen/Qwen3-4B-FP8", "criteria": [{"id": "F1", "axis": "instruction_following", "importance": "essential", "weight": 0.2941176470588235, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 사용자 요청을 직접적이고 빠짐없이 수행한다. [smoke:8c66c6]", "self_contained": true}, {"id": "F2", "axis": "correctness", "importance": "essential", "weight": 0.2941176470588235, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 사실 오류와 근거 없는 단정을 피하고 정확한 내용을 제공한다. [smoke:df001c]", "self_contained": true}, {"id": "F3", "axis": "completeness", "importance": "important", "weight": 0.20588235294117643, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 핵심 요소를 누락하지 않고 필요한 설명을 포함한다. [smoke:e0cad4]", "self_contained": true}, {"id": "F4", "axis": "korean_naturalness", "importance": "important", "weight": 0.20588235294117643, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 자연스럽고 읽기 쉬운 한국어 문장을 사용한다. [smoke:332dfc]", "self_contained": true}], "rar_items": [], "generation_metadata": {"fallback_used": "rrd_static_fallback", "errors": ["'\"satisfied\"'"], "auxiliary_sample_ids": ["sample_01", "sample_02", "sample_03", "sample_04", "sample_05", "sample_06", "sample_07", "sample_08"], "reference_guidance_used": true, "raw_output": "<think>\nOkay, I need to create a JSON with 8 criteria for evaluating the responses to the user's query about the impact of mountainous terrain on Korean hill forts and military strongholds. The user provided a reference response and several sample responses. My task is to come up with 8 binary criteria (YES/NO) that are specific to the prompt and not vague.\n\nFirst, I'll look at the reference response and the samples to identify key aspects that are important. The reference talks about the terrain's constraints, transparency and accessibility, strategic location, mountain culture, historical significance, etc. The samples elaborate on different aspects like the types of hill forts, technological advancements, military strategies, cultural aspects, and historical evolution.\n\nSo, the main elements seem to be: following the instruction, accuracy in historical context, technical details about fort construction, strategic analysis, cultural integration, historical significance, use of specific examples, and the overall structure of the response.\n\nLet me list possible criteria:\n\n1. Instruction Following: Does the response address the analysis of the impact of mountainous terrain on hill forts and military strongholds, and the historical significance?\n2. Historical Accuracy: Does the response correctly reference historical periods and events?\n3. Technical Detail: Does it include specific technical aspects of fort construction (like types of forts, materials, design features)?\n4. Strategic Analysis: Does it analyze the strategic advantages and disadvantages of the terrain in military contexts?\n5. Cultural Integration: Does it discuss the cultural aspects of hill forts, such as their role in society or religion?\n6. Use of Examples: Does it provide specific examples of hill forts from different historical periods?\n7. Historical Significance: Does it explain the long-term historical impact and legacy of these forts?\n8. Structure and Coherence: Is the response well-organized and logically presented?\n\nNow, I need to make sure each criterion is binary (YES/NO) and specific. Also, avoid generic advice. Let me check if these are covered in the samples. The reference and samples do mention specific examples, historical periods, technical details, cultural aspects, etc. So these criteria should work.\n\nI need to translate these into Korean and assign each a unique ID, axis, importance, and weight. The reference response is the upper bound, so the criteria should be based on that. The samples should be evaluated against these criteria. The final JSON should have 8 criteria with the specified fields.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 산지 지형이 산성 문화와 군사 요새 발달에 미친 영향을 분석하고, 역사적 의미를 고찰하는 데 집중되어야 합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"historical_accuracy\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 삼국시대, 고려, 조선 등 역사적 시기별 산성 발전을 정확히 반영해야 합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"technical_details\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 산성의 구조(테뫼식, 포곡식 등), 축성 기술(석축, 수리 시스템), 전략적 기능(보급, 수자원 관리)을 구체적으로 설명해야 합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"strategic_analysis\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 산지 지형이 군사 전략(지구전, 수성, 보급로 통제)에 미친 영향을 논리적으로 분석해야 합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"cultural_integration\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 산성과 종교(사찰), 사회(의병, 봉수 문화), 경관(성곽길, 산사)의 결합을 설명해야 합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"example_usage\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 고구려의 환도산성, 신라의 명활산성, 조선의 남한산성 등 구체적인 사례를 제시해야 합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"historical_significance\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 산성 문화가 국가 생존, 지역 공동체, 문화유산으로 이어진 역사적 의미를 명확히 설명해야 합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"structure_coherence\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 지형-전략-기술-문화의 연계를 중심으로 논리적으로 구조화되어야 합니다.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
