models.\n\nSo, possible criteria could be:\n\n1. Instruction Following: Does the response address the main points about Korean NLP challenges and model importance?\n2. Mention of Morphological Complexity: Does it discuss the complex morphology of Korean, like affixes and morphemes?\n3. Honorifics and Politeness: Does it cover the importance of honorifics in Korean communication?\n4. Spacing and Typographical Issues: Does it address the challenges of spacing and typographical variations in Korean?\n5. Loanwords and Code-switching: Does it mention the presence of loanwords and code-switching in Korean?\n6. Corpus and Data Limitations: Does it discuss the lack of large, high-quality Korean corpora?\n7. Domain Adaptation: Does it talk about the need for domain-specific models in Korean NLP?\n8. Cultural and Social Context: Does it address the cultural and social aspects of Korean communication in NLP?\n\nI need to make sure each criterion is specific to the prompt and can be evaluated as YES or NO. Let me check if these are covered in the samples. The samples do mention all these points, so these criteria should work. Now, I'll structure them into JSON with the required fields.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 한국어 NLP의 난점과 모델 개발 중요성을 명확히 설명합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"morphological_complexity\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 한국어의 교착어, 조사-어미 결합, 형태 변화를 구체적으로 설명합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"honorifics_and_politeness\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 공손도, 말투 체계, 존칭어의 문화적 중요성을 다룹니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"spacing_and_typographical_issues\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 띄어쓰기 불안정, 반말/구어체, 이모티콘 등 텍스트 변이를 언급합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"loanwords_and_code_switching\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 외래어, 신조어, 코드스위칭의 영향을 구체적으로 분석합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"corpus_and_data_limitations\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 한국어 말뭉치 부족, 데이터 편향, 벤치마크 한계를 설명합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"domain_adaptation\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 도메인별(법, 의학, 커뮤니티) 모델 적응의 필요성을 강조합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"cultural_and_social_context\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 한국어의 사회언어학적 특성(방언, 세대 차이)을 모델 설계에 반영해야 함을 강조합니다.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
