mmendations, categorizing them into genres like fiction, essays, self-help, and non-fiction, along with tips on reading habits.\n\nThe key points from the reference and samples are: following the instruction to recommend books, providing a variety of genres, explaining why fiction is helpful, and giving practical reading tips. The criteria should be binary (yes/no) and specific to the prompt.\n\nSo, the criteria should focus on whether the response follows the instruction, includes a variety of genres, explains the benefits of fiction, provides specific book recommendations, includes practical reading tips, addresses both parts of the question, ensures the recommendations are relevant to the user's situation (high school senior, post-exam), and whether the response is well-structured and easy to follow.\n\nNow, I need to translate these into 8 specific, binary criteria. Let me list them out:\n\n1. Instruction Following: Does the response directly answer both questions about book recommendations and the effectiveness of fiction?\n2. Genre Variety: Does the response include a range of genres (fiction, non-fiction, essays, etc.)?\n3. Explanation of Benefits: Does it explain why fiction helps with vocabulary and knowledge?\n4. Specific Book Recommendations: Are specific books mentioned with titles and authors?\n5. Practical Tips: Are there actionable reading tips provided?\n6. Relevance to User's Situation: Are the recommendations suitable for a high school senior post-exam?\n7. Structure and Clarity: Is the response well-organized and easy to follow?\n8. Addressing Both Questions: Does the response cover both parts of the user's query (book recommendations and fiction effectiveness)?\n\nEach of these can be a criterion. Now, I need to make sure they are binary (yes/no) and not vague. For example, \"Genre Variety\" would be yes if the response includes multiple genres, no otherwise. Similarly, \"Specific Book Recommendations\" would be yes if specific titles are given, no if it's just general advice.\n\nI should check the sample responses to see if they meet these criteria. For instance, the first sample response includes multiple genres, specific books, explains the benefits of fiction, and provides tips. So, each of these would be a \"yes\" for that sample. The reference response also includes specific books and explains the benefits.\n\nNow, I need to structure this into the JSON format as specified, with each criterion having an ID, axis, importance, weight, polarity, text in Korean, and self_contained. The importance is essential, weight 0.5, polarity positive. The text should be concise and specific.\n\nI need to make sure that the criteria are not overlapping and cover the key aspects of the evaluation. Let me finalize the 8 criteria based on the above analysis.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 두 가지 질문 모두에 대한 구체적인 답변을 포함합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"genre_coverage\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 소설, 에세이, 교양서, 자기관리 등 다양한 장르의 책을 추천합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"benefit_explanation\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 소설이 어휘력과 지식 향상에 어떻게 도움되는지 구체적으로 설명합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"specific_recommendations\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 특정 책의 제목과 저자를 명시적으로 제시합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"practical_tips\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 독서 습관을 형성하는 실용적인 팁(예: 50페이지 룰, 단어 처리 방법)을 포함합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"user_relevance\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 수능 끝난 고3 대상의 정서적 여유와 학습 재개에 맞춘 추천을 포함합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"structure_clarity\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 질문별로 구분하고, 내용이 논리적으로 정리되어 있습니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"balanced_answer\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 소설만 읽는 경우의 한계와 장르 혼합의 효과를 설명합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
