mplementation.\n\nThe criteria must be specific to the problem and binary (YES/NO). Let me think of the essential aspects:\n\n1. **Correct Implementation of Both Methods**: The response must include both methods. If either is missing, it's a no.\n\n2. **Time Complexity for Both Methods**: Each method's time complexity must be correctly stated. For example, O(n) for the linear scan and O(n²) for brute force.\n\n3. **Function Signature**: The solution function must take a list of prices as input. If the function is not correctly defined, it's a no.\n\n4. **Handling Edge Cases**: The response should handle cases where no profit is possible (like when prices are strictly decreasing). The sample responses mention returning 0 in such cases.\n\n5. **Correctness of Examples**: The examples provided in the samples should match the expected outputs. For instance, the first example should return 6.\n\n6. **Explanation of the Methods**: The explanation must clearly describe each method's approach. If the explanation is vague or incorrect, it's a no.\n\n7. **Code Correctness**: The code for both methods must be syntactically correct. Any syntax errors would make it a no.\n\n8. **Time Complexity Accuracy**: The time complexity for each method must be accurately stated. For example, O(n²) for brute force and O(n) for the linear scan.\n\nNow, I need to translate these into 8 specific criteria. Let me check if these are all covered and if they are binary. Also, ensure they are not generic. For example, \"correct implementation of both methods\" is specific. Similarly, \"time complexity for both methods\" is specific.\n\nI need to make sure each criterion is a yes/no question. For example, \"Does the response include both methods?\" is a yes/no. Similarly, \"Are the time complexities correctly stated for both methods?\" is another yes/no.\n\nI should also check if the criteria are not overlapping. For instance, code correctness and function signature are separate. Also, handling edge cases is a separate criterion.\n\nNow, I'll structure the 8 criteria based on these points.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 두 가지 방법(브루트포스 및 선형 스캔)을 모두 포함하고 있습니까?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"각 방법의 시간 복잡도가 O(n²)과 O(n)으로 정확히 표기되어 있습니까?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"code_quality\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"모든 코드가 파이썬 문법에 맞게 작성되어 있습니까?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"edge_case_handling\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"가격이 내림차순일 때 0을 반환하는 코드가 포함되어 있습니까?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"example_accuracy\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"예시 입력 [1,5,3,7,4]의 출력이 6으로 정확히 표기되어 있습니까?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"method_explanation\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"브루트포스와 선형 스캔의 알고리즘 설명이 명확히 구분되어 있습니까?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"function_signature\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"solution(prices) 함수가 정확히 정의되어 있습니까?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"code_correctness\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"모든 코드가 주가가 10억 이하의 양수 조건을 충족하는지 검증되어 있습니까?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
