{"prompt_id": "prompt_00d0479e77e5", "pair_id": "pair_32fc2409b8ab", "method": "rrd_pairwise_reference", "generator_family": "qwen_small", "generator_model": "Qwen/Qwen3-4B-FP8", "criteria": [{"id": "F1", "axis": "instruction_following", "importance": "essential", "weight": 0.2941176470588235, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 사용자 요청을 직접적이고 빠짐없이 수행한다. [smoke:20f0ae]", "self_contained": true}, {"id": "F2", "axis": "correctness", "importance": "essential", "weight": 0.2941176470588235, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 사실 오류와 근거 없는 단정을 피하고 정확한 내용을 제공한다. [smoke:cb02d9]", "self_contained": true}, {"id": "F3", "axis": "completeness", "importance": "important", "weight": 0.20588235294117643, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 핵심 요소를 누락하지 않고 필요한 설명을 포함한다. [smoke:18fa0a]", "self_contained": true}, {"id": "F4", "axis": "korean_naturalness", "importance": "important", "weight": 0.20588235294117643, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 자연스럽고 읽기 쉬운 한국어 문장을 사용한다. [smoke:364ec3]", "self_contained": true}], "rar_items": [], "generation_metadata": {"fallback_used": "rrd_static_fallback", "errors": ["'\"satisfied\"'"], "auxiliary_sample_ids": ["sample_01", "sample_02", "sample_03", "sample_04", "sample_05", "sample_06", "sample_07", "sample_08"], "reference_guidance_used": true, "raw_output": "<think>\nOkay, I need to create 8 criteria for evaluating the responses to the user's request about improving support policies for small businesses in South Korea. The user provided a reference response and several sample responses. The criteria should be specific to the prompt, binary (YES/NO), and not vague.\n\nFirst, I'll look at the reference response. It covers three main areas: rent relief, business consulting, and social safety nets. The sample responses also elaborate on these areas with specific measures like rent-linked contracts, digital tools, and insurance programs.\n\nFor the criteria, I need to ensure each one checks if the response addresses the key points. Let's start with instruction following. The response should directly address the three areas mentioned. So, the first criterion could be whether the response includes all three areas: rent relief, business consulting, and social safety nets.\n\nNext, the response should propose specific, actionable ideas. So, another criterion could be if the response includes concrete measures for each area, like rent-linked contracts or digital tools.\n\nAnother point is whether the response is data-driven. The samples mention using data for dashboards and performance metrics, so a criterion could check if data is used to support the proposals.\n\nThen, the response should have a clear structure. The reference and samples are well-organized, so a criterion could check if the response is structured into sections or clear points.\n\nAlso, the response should be comprehensive, covering all aspects of the problem. The samples include detailed measures for each area, so a criterion could check if the response covers all necessary aspects without missing key elements.\n\nAnother criterion could be whether the response includes a timeline or implementation plan. The samples have roadmaps and phases, so checking if the response has a clear plan for implementation.\n\nAdditionally, the response should address potential risks or challenges. The samples mention risk mitigation strategies, so a criterion could check if the response includes such considerations.\n\nLastly, the response should be feasible and practical. The samples propose realistic solutions, so a criterion could check if the proposals are realistic and can be implemented.\n\nNow, I need to translate these into 8 binary criteria. Each should be specific to the prompt and check for the presence of certain elements. Let me list them out:\n\n1. Instruction Following: Does the response address all three areas (rent relief, business consulting, social safety nets)?\n2. Specificity: Are there concrete, actionable ideas for each area?\n3. Data-Driven: Does the response use data or metrics to support the proposals?\n4. Structure: Is the response well-organized into clear sections or points?\n5. Comprehensive: Does the response cover all necessary aspects without missing key elements?\n6. Implementation Plan: Does the response include a timeline or phased approach?\n7. Risk Mitigation: Does the response address potential risks or challenges?\n8. Feasibility: Are the proposals realistic and practical?\n\nI need to make sure each criterion is binary (YES/NO) and specific. Now, I'll format them into JSON as per the user's instructions.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 임대료 부담 완화, 경영 컨설팅 지원, 사회 안전망 강화의 세 축을 모두 포함합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"specificity\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 각 축에 구체적인 실행 방안(예: 매출연동 임대, 데이터 대시보드)을 제시합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"data_driven\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 카드매출 데이터, 임대료 지수 등 실데이터 기반의 분석·결론을 포함합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"structure\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 세부 항목별 구조화된 분석(예: 1) 임대료 부담 완화, 2) 경영 컨설팅 등)로 구성됩니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"comprehensiveness\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 정책 재원, 인센티브, 데이터 거버넌스, 성과지표까지 전반적인 시스템 설계를 포함합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"implementation_plan\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 단기(6개월), 중기(1~3년), 장기(3~5년) 로드맵을 구체적으로 제시합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"risk_mitigation\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 임대료 급등 억제, 데이터 남용 방지, 도덕적 해이 예방 등 위험 요소를 대응합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"feasibility\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 세제 연동, 민관 협력, 데이터 표준화 등 현실적 실행 가능성을 포함합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
