, and the role of stars and night.\n\nFirst, I need to identify key elements that the reference and samples share. The main themes are perseverance, hope, stars as symbols, personal growth, and the journey through challenges. Each criterion should check if these elements are present.\n\n1. **Instruction Following**: Does the response directly address the prompt about the journey of a young person inspired by the poems? The reference and samples all do this, so this is essential.\n\n2. **Use of Stars and Night Imagery**: The reference and samples use stars and night as central motifs. This is a key element.\n\n3. **Personal Growth and Resilience**: The poems show the character overcoming obstacles, so checking if this is present.\n\n4. **Hope and Dream Themes**: The reference and samples emphasize hope and dreams, so this is important.\n\n5. **Poetic Structure and Flow**: The reference has a consistent structure, so checking if the response maintains a poetic flow.\n\n6. **Emotional Depth**: The samples show deep emotions, so checking if the response conveys emotional depth.\n\n7. **Symbolism and Metaphor**: The use of metaphors like stars as guidance is key.\n\n8. **Originality and Creativity**: The reference and samples have unique takes, so checking for originality.\n\nNow, I need to make sure each criterion is binary and specific. For example, \"Use of Stars and Night Imagery\" would check if stars and night are central. \"Emotional Depth\" would check if the response conveys deep emotions. Each criterion should be a yes/no check based on the presence of the element.\n\nI need to avoid generic advice and ensure each criterion is tied directly to the prompt. The reference and samples all have these elements, so the criteria should reflect that. Let me structure the JSON accordingly.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 '서시'와 '별 헤는 밤'의 모티프를 명확히 반영하여 청년의 꿈과 희망을 향한 여정을 시적 구조로 표현한다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"star_night_imagery\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 별, 밤, 하늘 등의 이미지로 청년의 내면적 여정을 시각화하고, 자연의 흐름과 연결시킨다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"resilience\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 어려움 속에서도 꿈을 지키는 청년의 내면적 투쟁을 시적 대화체로 드러낸다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"hope_theme\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 희망이 단순한 선언이 아니라, 일상의 작은 선택들로 이어지는 체계를 시적 구조로 표현한다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"poetic_flow\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 시적 리듬과 반복 구조를 통해 청년의 여정을 연속적인 이미지 흐름으로 구성한다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"emotional_depth\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 청년의 부끄러움, 희망, 내면적 갈등을 시적 대화체로 깊이 탐색한다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"symbolism\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 별, 빛, 어둠 등의 상징을 청년의 내면적 여정과 직접적으로 연결시킨다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"originality\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 전통 시적 구조를 벗어나, 청년의 내면적 변화를 시적 흐름으로 독창적으로 재구성한다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
