on disputed claims. So, one criterion could be whether the response names a tribe that is historically known to have not used fire.\n\nAnother point is whether the response explains why they didn't use fire, like cultural reasons. The reference mentions their fear of fire and myths. So a criterion could be if the response includes a reason for not using fire.\n\nAlso, the reference provides a timeline (1970s onwards they started using fire). So a criterion could check if the response includes a historical timeline or period when they didn't use fire.\n\nAnother aspect is the accuracy of the information. Some samples might be based on myths or disputed sources. So a criterion could be whether the response is based on reliable historical records.\n\nAlso, the response should be self-contained, not relying on external sources. The reference doesn't mention external sources, so a criterion could check if the response is self-contained.\n\nAdditionally, the response should be specific to the tribe mentioned. For example, if the sample says \"Tasmanian Aboriginals\" but there's debate about that, the criterion could check if the tribe is clearly identified and not ambiguous.\n\nAnother point is whether the response addresses the query directly, not just listing tribes. The reference does that, so a criterion could check if the response directly answers the question.\n\nLastly, the response should be concise but informative. The reference is detailed but to the point. A criterion could check if the response is concise and provides necessary details without unnecessary information.\n\nNow, compiling these into 8 criteria. Each must be binary and specific. Let me list them:\n\n1. Correctly identifies a tribe that historically did not use fire.\n2. Includes a reason for not using fire (e.g., cultural beliefs, fear).\n3. Provides a historical timeline when the tribe didn't use fire.\n4. Based on reliable historical records, not myths or disputed claims.\n5. Self-contained, without external sources.\n6. Clearly identifies the tribe without ambiguity.\n7. Directly answers the query without irrelevant information.\n8. Concise and provides necessary details without excess.\n\nI need to make sure each is prompt-specific and binary. Let me check if these fit. The reference response includes all these elements, while some samples might miss some. For example, the sample \"Tasmanian Aboriginals\" might be disputed, so the fourth criterion would flag that. The Önge example is mentioned as using fire but not making it, so that's a different case. The criteria should cover these aspects.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 역사적으로 불을 사용하지 못한 부족을 명확히 지정해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"accuracy\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 신뢰할 수 있는 역사적 기록에 기반해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"contextual_detail\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 부족이 불을 사용하지 않은 시기나 이유를 설명해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"specificity\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 특정 부족 이름을 명확히 제공해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"relevance\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 질문에 직접 답변해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"consistency\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 역사적 사실과 일치해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"clarity\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 명확하고 구체적인 정보를 제공해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"completeness\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 질문에 필요한 모든 정보를 포함해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
