t. They should focus on whether the response follows the instruction, uses the right tools, includes necessary steps, etc.\n\nLooking at the sample responses, they mention specific tools like VTube Studio, Inworld Studio, OBS, ElevenLabs, etc. So one criterion could be whether the response includes the correct tools for a beginner.\n\nAnother point is whether the response provides a clear, step-by-step guide without requiring programming. The reference response does that, so that's a good criterion.\n\nAlso, the sample responses include practical examples and a quick start guide, so a criterion about providing a practical, actionable plan could be important.\n\nI need to ensure each criterion is specific and not generic. For example, instead of saying \"good structure,\" it should be something like \"includes a step-by-step guide for a beginner without programming.\"\n\nLet me list possible criteria:\n\n1. Instruction Following: Does the response follow the user's request to create an AI YouTuber without programming?\n2. Tool Specificity: Does it mention specific tools like VTube Studio, Inworld Studio, OBS, etc.?\n3. Practical Steps: Does it provide clear, actionable steps for a beginner?\n4. No Programming Required: Does it avoid any programming concepts or steps?\n5. Clear Structure: Is the response organized into logical steps or sections?\n6. Beginner-Friendly: Does it use language and examples suitable for a complete novice?\n7. Includes Necessary Components: Does it cover all essential parts like avatar creation, tracking, audio, etc.?\n8. Realistic Timeline: Does it provide a realistic, achievable timeline for a beginner?\n\nNow, I need to make sure each is binary and specific. For example, \"Includes a step-by-step guide for a beginner without programming\" is specific and binary.\n\nI should check the reference and sample responses to ensure these criteria are covered. The reference response does mention steps, but the samples are more detailed with specific tools and steps. So the criteria should reflect that.\n\nI think that's a good start. Now, I'll structure the JSON with these criteria, ensuring each has an ID, axis, importance, weight, polarity, and text in Korean.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 '코딩 1도 모르는 초보자에게 AI 버튜버 만들기'를 위한 구체적인 단계를 제공한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"tool_specificity\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 VTube Studio, Inworld Studio, OBS, ElevenLabs 등 초보자 친화적인 도구를 명시적으로 언급한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"practical_steps\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 'PNG 튜버'부터 '3D 아바타'까지 단계별로 실행 가능한 실용적인 루트를 제시한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"no_programming_required\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 프로그래밍 개념이나 코드를 전혀 포함하지 않고, 노코드/저코드 방법만 설명한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"clear_structure\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 '아바타 만들기', '트래킹', '음성', 'AI 대화' 등 핵심 구성 요소를 구조화된 단계로 나누어 설명한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"beginner_friendly\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 '마이크', '웹캠', 'VRoid Studio' 등 초보자에게 친화적인 장비와 도구를 중심으로 설명한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"necessary_components\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 아바타, 트래킹, 음성 합성, AI 대화, 방송 송출 등 AI 버튜버를 구성하는 핵심 요소를 모두 포함한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"realistic_timeline\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 '1일차', '2~3일차', '1주일 내' 등 구체적인 시간 범위를 제시해 실현 가능성을 보장한다.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
