ther OS options. The sample responses also cover similar steps, including BIOS settings, FDISK, formatting, installing drivers, and dual-booting.\n\nNow, I need to identify the key aspects that the evaluation should focus on. The reference response and samples all include steps like correct BIOS settings, proper FDISK usage, correct formatting commands, driver installation order, and OS selection for gaming.\n\nSo, possible criteria could be:\n\n1. Instruction Following: Did the response follow the user's instructions to format C and not touch D/E/F?\n2. BIOS Settings: Correctly mentioned setting CD-ROM as first boot device.\n3. FDISK Usage: Proper steps for partitioning without deleting D/E/F.\n4. Formatting Commands: Correct use of 'format c:' and other commands.\n5. Driver Installation Order: Correct sequence for drivers (chipset, graphics, etc.).\n6. OS Selection for Gaming: Correctly advised Windows 98 over ME/XP for old games.\n7. Dual Boot Guidance: If the response included dual boot steps.\n8. Safety Precautions: Mentioned backing up data and not formatting D/E/F.\n\nI need to make sure each criterion is specific, binary, and not generic. Let me check if these are covered in the samples. The reference response and samples all mention BIOS settings, FDISK, formatting, driver order, OS selection, and dual boot. So these 8 points should cover the key aspects.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 사용자의 'C 드라이브만 포맷하고 D/E/F를 유지하라'는 요청을 명확히 따르고, 플로피 디스크 사용 금지 요구사항을 포함하고 있나요?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"bios_configuration\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 BIOS에서 CD-ROM을 1순위 부팅 장치로 설정하는 방법을 구체적으로 설명했나요?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"partition_management\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 D/E/F 파티션을 삭제하지 않고 C 드라이브만 포맷하는 방법을 명확히 설명했나요?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"formatting_commands\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 'format c:' 명령어와 관련된 경고 메시지 처리(예: Y 입력)를 포함하고 있나요?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"driver_installation_order\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 메인보드 드라이버 → 그래픽 드라이버 → 사운드 드라이버 순서를 명확히 설명했나요?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"os_recommendation\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 고전 게임용으로 Windows 98을 권장하고, XP/ME의 단점을 명확히 비교했나요?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"dual_boot_guidance\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 듀얼 부팅(98 + XP) 방법을 단계별로 설명했나요?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"safety_precautions\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 데이터 백업의 중요성과 D/E/F 파티션 손상 방지 조언을 포함했나요?\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
