mes.\n\nThe rubric needs to be specific, binary (YES/NO), and not vague. Let me think about the essential aspects of a good poem in this context. \n\n1. **Instruction Following**: Does the poem directly address the theme of modern sorrows and hopes, inspired by \"Ga Shi Ri\"? The reference uses a structured format, while samples vary but still touch on the theme. So, this is essential.\n\n2. **Thematic Relevance**: Does the poem incorporate elements from \"Ga Shi Ri\" (like nature imagery, emotional depth) and modern contexts (like urban life, daily struggles)? The reference uses nature and contrast, while samples use urban metaphors. This is important.\n\n3. **Imagery and Metaphor**: Does the poem use vivid, relatable imagery that connects traditional and modern elements? The samples use everyday scenes, which is key.\n\n4. **Emotional Depth**: Does the poem convey both sorrow and hope, as required? The reference has a clear contrast, while samples vary but aim for that balance.\n\n5. **Structure and Form**: Does the poem maintain a structure similar to \"Ga Shi Ri,\" perhaps with stanzas or a lyrical flow? The reference uses stanzas, while some samples are more free-form. This is important for adherence to the original form.\n\n6. **Originality and Creativity**: Does the poem offer a unique perspective that blends traditional and modern elements? The samples show creativity in different ways.\n\n7. **Language and Style**: Is the language poetic, with a balance between traditional and modern diction? The reference uses a mix, while samples vary in style.\n\n8. **Cohesion and Flow**: Does the poem maintain a logical flow that connects the themes of sorrow and hope? The reference has a clear progression, while some samples may have more fragmented flow.\n\nWait, the user wants 8 criteria. Let me check if these 8 cover the essentials. Maybe I need to adjust. For example, \"Instruction Following\" could be split into thematic relevance and structure. But the user wants 8, so I need to ensure each is distinct and binary. Let me finalize the criteria based on the analysis.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"시는 '가시리'의 정서(자연의 아름다움, 감정의 깊이)와 현대인의 애환과 희망을 결합한 구조를 갖추고 있어야 합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"thematic_relevance\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"시는 현대 생활(도시, 퇴근, 소통의 어려움 등)과 감정적 갈등을 반영한 상황을 자연스럽게 표현해야 합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"imagery_and_metaphor\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"시는 자연(달, 바람, 물)과 현대적 이미지(편의점, 지하철, 알림)를 결합한 독특한 비유를 사용해야 합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"emotional_balance\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"시는 애환(고독, 소통의 어려움)과 희망(새로운 시작, 작은 기쁨)을 균형 있게 표현해야 합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"structural_coherence\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"시는 '가시리'의 시조(단순한 구조, 반복적 형식)를 유지하거나 현대적 형식과 조화를 이뤄야 합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"originality\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.1,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"시는 전통과 현대를 연결하는 독특한 해석이나 표현 방식을 보여야 합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"language_quality\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.1,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"시는 시적 언어(시적 이미지, 은유, 반복)와 현대적 표현을 자연스럽게 결합해야 합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"flow_and_cohesion\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.1,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"시는 감정의 전개가 자연스럽고, 주제 간 연결이 명확해야 합니다.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
