es are: vocabulary differences, slang and jargon, honorifics, speed of speech, understanding of social norms, use of foreign words, and the emotional aspect of adaptation.\n\nNow, I need to translate these into 8 specific criteria. Each should be a binary yes/no check. Let me list them:\n\n1. **Instruction Following - Vocabulary Differences**: Does the response address the vocabulary differences between North and South Korea?\n2. **Instruction Following - Slang/Jargon**: Does it mention the challenges of understanding slang and jargon in South Korea?\n3. **Instruction Following - Honorifics**: Does it cover the difficulties with honorifics and formality levels?\n4. **Instruction Following - Speech Speed**: Does it discuss the issue of speech speed and rhythm differences?\n5. **Instruction Following - Social Norms**: Does it address the adaptation to social norms and etiquette in South Korea?\n6. **Instruction Following - Foreign Words**: Does it mention the challenges of using foreign words and loanwords?\n7. **Instruction Following - Emotional Adaptation**: Does it touch on the emotional and psychological aspects of adapting to the new language environment?\n8. **Instruction Following - Practical Solutions**: Does it provide practical strategies or solutions for overcoming these language barriers?\n\nI need to make sure each criterion is specific to the prompt and not vague. Also, they should be binary. Let me check if these are all covered in the reference and samples. Yes, each of these points is addressed in the samples. Now, I'll structure them into the JSON format as specified.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 남북한 언어 차이로 인한 의사소통 어려움과 사회 적응 과정에서의 언어적 도전을 구체적으로 설명합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 외래어, 신조어, 줄임말 등 남한 사회에서 사용되는 특수 언어 표현의 이해 어려움을 다룹니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 높임말 사용의 어려움과 존댓말/반말 전환의 사회적 맥락을 정확히 묘사합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 은어, 속어, 문화적 차이로 인한 소외감과 사회적 적응의 어려움을 구체적으로 설명합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 언어적 도전 속에서의 감정적 경험(불안, 좌절, 용기)을 공감적으로 전달합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 언어 적응을 위한 실질적 전략(단어 학습, 듣기 연습, 안전한 대화 환경)을 구체적으로 제시합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 남북한 언어 차이가 사회적 관계 형성과 정체성에 미치는 영향을 체계적으로 분석합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 언어적 장벽을 넘어 '다른 말맛'을 존중하고 공존하는 사회적 태도를 강조합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
