 types and sleeping positions.\n\nSo, the key factors from the reference and samples include: size and space, comfort (mattress firmness), material type (spring, memory foam, latex, hybrid), motion isolation, edge support, temperature regulation, durability and warranty, and safety/health considerations.\n\nI need to make sure each criterion is specific to the prompt and can be evaluated as a yes/no. Let me list possible criteria:\n\n1. **Instruction Following**: Does the response address all the key factors mentioned in the reference and samples? (Yes/No)\n2. **Size and Space Consideration**: Does the response mention factors like bed size, room dimensions, and space for movement? (Yes/No)\n3. **Material Type and Performance**: Does the response discuss different mattress materials (spring, memory foam, etc.) and their characteristics? (Yes/No)\n4. **Motion Isolation**: Does the response address how to reduce motion transfer between sleepers? (Yes/No)\n5. **Edge Support**: Does the response mention the importance of edge support for stability and comfort? (Yes/No)\n6. **Temperature Regulation**: Does the response cover factors affecting temperature, like ventilation or cooling features? (Yes/No)\n7. **Durability and Warranty**: Does the response discuss the longevity of the mattress and warranty terms? (Yes/No)\n8. **Health and Safety Considerations**: Does the response include factors like allergens, materials safety, and certifications? (Yes/No)\n\nNow, I need to check if these are binary and specific. Each of these points can be evaluated as yes or no based on whether the response includes the factor. The reference and samples do cover these aspects, so the criteria should be valid. I'll structure them in JSON with the required fields.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 침대 구매 시 고려해야 할 요소들을 명확히 서술하고, 각 요소의 중요성을 설명합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"size_and_space\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.25,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 방 크기, 동선, 침대 사이즈 선택에 대한 고려 요소를 포함합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"material_performance\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.25,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 스프링, 메모리폼, 라텍스, 하이브리드 등 매트리스 소재별 특성과 장단점을 설명합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"motion_isolation\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 동반자와 함께 수면 시 진동 전달을 줄이는 요소(예: 메모리폼, 하이브리드)를 언급합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"edge_support\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 침대 가장자리 지지(엣지 서포트)의 중요성과 구조적 고려 요소를 포함합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"temperature_regulation\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 온도 조절(통기성, 쿨링 커버)과 체온 관리에 관련된 요소를 설명합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"durability_warranty\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 매트리스 내구성, 처짐 저항, 보증 조건(처짐 허용치)을 언급합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"health_safety\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 알레르기, 화학물질, 인증(예: CertiPUR-US, OEKO-TEX) 등 건강 및 안전 관련 요소를 포함합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
