outine, and specific techniques for handling different conditions.\n\nSo, the main themes are:\n1. Environmental differences (practice vs. real course)\n2. Mental pressure and stress\n3. Shot variety and adaptability\n4. Course management and strategy\n5. Equipment and ball differences\n6. Routine and consistency\n7. Physical factors like stamina and hydration\n8. Specific techniques for handling different conditions (like slopes, wind, etc.)\n\nI need to make sure each criterion is specific and binary. Let me list possible criteria:\n\n1. **Environmental Differences**: Does the response address the difference between practice and real course environments?\n2. **Mental Pressure**: Does it mention the psychological pressure of real courses?\n3. **Shot Variety**: Does it discuss the need for varied shots in real courses?\n4. **Course Management**: Does it cover course-specific strategies and management?\n5. **Equipment/Ball Differences**: Does it note differences in equipment or balls used?\n6. **Routine Consistency**: Does it address maintaining a consistent routine?\n7. **Physical Factors**: Does it mention physical aspects like stamina or hydration?\n8. **Specific Techniques**: Does it include techniques for handling slopes, wind, etc.?\n\nNow, I need to phrase each as a binary question in Korean. Let me check if these are specific enough and not generic. For example, \"Environmental Differences\" is specific to the prompt. \"Mental Pressure\" is also relevant. \"Shot Variety\" is covered in the samples. \"Course Management\" is a key point. \"Equipment/Ball Differences\" is mentioned in some samples. \"Routine Consistency\" is another aspect. \"Physical Factors\" like stamina and hydration are important. \"Specific Techniques\" for handling conditions like slopes and wind.\n\nI think these eight criteria cover the main points from the reference and samples. Now, I'll structure them into JSON with the required format.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 연습장과 실제 코스의 환경 차이를 명확히 설명합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 심리적 압박감이 실제 코스에서 더 높다고 분석합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 다양한 샷 유형(베이커, 어프로치 등)의 필요성을 설명합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 코스 매니지먼트(핀 선택, 해저드 회피) 전략을 제시합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 연습장 볼과 실제 볼의 차이를 인지하는 것이 중요하다고 강조합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 루틴 유지와 일관된 스윙 패턴의 중요성을 설명합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 체력 관리(수분, 간식)와 템포 유지의 필요성을 언급합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 경사, 바람, 잔디 상태 등 구체적 조건 대응 기술을 제시합니다.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
