g at the sample responses, they all include key points like the demand for the cultural centers, the status of the Siheung cultural center plan, the budget details, the strategy to use the area for education and culture, the role of cultural infrastructure in attracting tourists, and the isolated island situation.\n\nSo, the main elements to check in the responses are: whether they mention the demand for the cultural centers, the status of the Siheung plan, the budget figures, the strategy for education vs. culture, the accessibility and cultural activities, the role of tourists, the isolated island situation, and the need for cultural infrastructure.\n\nEach criterion should be specific and binary (yes/no). Let me list them out:\n\n1. Mention of the demand for multi-purpose cultural center and citizens center.\n2. Status of the Siheung cultural center plan (only plan, not implemented).\n3. Budget details (1.2 trillion, land and construction costs).\n4. Strategy to use the area for education (Baegrod) and culture (Wolgok).\n5. Accessibility and cultural activities to attract tourists.\n6. Role of cultural infrastructure in boosting local economy and tourism.\n7. Isolated island situation due to surrounding roads.\n8. Need for cultural infrastructure to overcome the isolated situation.\n\nEach of these points is specific and can be evaluated as yes or no. They are all directly related to the reference response and the samples. I need to make sure they are not vague and are specific to the prompt. Also, avoid generic advice. The criteria should be based on the content of the responses, not on general writing quality. So, these eight points should cover the key aspects that the reference and samples address.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"멀티플렉스 종합 문화센터와 주민센터 수요를 명확히 반영했는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"fact_accuracy\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"시흥시 문화예술센터 계획 규모(1,200억 원, 토지비/건축비)를 정확히 전달했는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"strategic_suggestion\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"배곧(교육) vs 월곶(문화) 전략을 구체적으로 제안했는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"contextual_relevance\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"월곶의 접근성과 '섬' 구조가 문화 활성화에 미치는 영향을 설명했는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"tourism_implication\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"중국 관광객의 문화 향유와 상권 활성화를 연결했는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"structural_analysis\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"도로망으로 둘러싸인 지역의 고립성과 문화 인프라의 역할을 비교했는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"economic_impact\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"문화 기반 확충이 지역 경제 활성화에 어떻게 기여할 것인지 설명했는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"comprehensive_coverage\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"주민 문화 수요와 외부 관광객 유치의 복합적 필요성을 모두 다루었는가?\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
