re essential.\n\nLooking at the reference, the dialogue is structured with a clear setting, characters, and a logical progression of ideas. The samples vary in how they handle the dialogue, some more detailed, others more abstract. The main criteria should be binary (yes/no) and specific to the task.\n\nPossible criteria could be: instruction following (whether the response follows the user's request), character consistency, dialogue coherence, historical accuracy, use of specific terms, logical flow, depth of discussion, and adherence to the script format.\n\nWait, the user mentioned that the criteria should be prompt-specific and binary. So each criterion must be a yes/no check. Let me think of 8 specific aspects.\n\n1. Instruction Following: Does the response create a script with a dialogue between the scholars as requested?\n2. Character Consistency: Are the characters' names and roles accurately represented?\n3. Historical Accuracy: Does the dialogue reflect the historical context and philosophical views of the Joseon scholars?\n4. Dialogue Coherence: Is the conversation logically structured and flows naturally?\n5. Use of Specific Terms: Does the response use appropriate terminology related to the scholars' fields (e.g., realpolitik, practical learning)?\n6. Script Format: Is the response structured as a script with scene headings and dialogue?\n7. Depth of Discussion: Does the dialogue delve into the philosophical and practical aspects of the scholars' views?\n8. Logical Flow: Does the conversation have a clear progression and conclusion?\n\nI need to make sure each criterion is specific and can be evaluated as yes/no. Also, avoid generic advice. Let me check if these are all prompt-specific and binary. Yes, each can be assessed as yes or no. Now, translate these into Korean with the required structure.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 조선 시대 실학자들의 대화를 스크립트 형식으로 구체적으로 표현했는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"character_consistency\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"등장인물의 역할과 이름이 실제 실학자와 일치하며, 대화에서 일관된 성격을 보였는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"historical_accuracy\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"대화 내용이 조선 시대 실학자의 사상과 실천적 관점에 부합했는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"dialogue_coherence\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"대화가 논리적 흐름을 가지며, 각 인물의 의견이 자연스럽게 교차했는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"script_format\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"스크립트 형식(장면 분할, 대화 태그, 설정 설명)이 명확히 구현되었는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"depth_of_discussion\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"실학자의 실천적 사상(예: 농업, 경제, 교육)에 대한 구체적 논의가 포함되었는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"logical_flow\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"대화가 시작부터 종결까지 일관된 주제와 결론을 이끌어내었는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"philosophical_consistency\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"실학자들의 대화가 실용주의와 이론적 사상의 균형을 유지했는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
