detailed, listing various issues and specific programs. The sample responses also have similar structures, each detailing the main challenges and then the proposed policies. So the criteria should focus on whether the response addresses these aspects.\n\nThe first criterion should be about following the instruction. The response must explain the challenges and propose policies. So, \"Does the response clearly explain the challenges and propose joint policies?\" That's essential.\n\nNext, the second criterion could be about the comprehensiveness of the challenges addressed. The response should cover a wide range of issues like language barriers, education, employment, etc. So, \"Does the response cover a broad range of challenges in social integration?\"\n\nThird, the response should include specific policies. So, \"Are specific, actionable policies and programs proposed for the government and local communities?\"\n\nFourth, the response should address the collaboration between government and local communities. So, \"Does the response emphasize joint efforts between government and local communities?\"\n\nFifth, the response should include data or metrics for evaluation. The reference and samples mention KPIs, so \"Does the response include measurable indicators or evaluation criteria for the proposed policies?\"\n\nSixth, the response should be structured logically. The samples have sections like challenges, policies, implementation steps. So, \"Is the response well-organized with clear sections for challenges and solutions?\"\n\nSeventh, the response should be culturally sensitive. The samples mention cultural aspects, so \"Does the response consider cultural sensitivity and inclusivity in the proposed policies?\"\n\nEighth, the response should be practical and feasible. The samples have realistic programs, so \"Are the proposed policies and programs realistic and implementable in practice?\"\n\nI need to make sure each criterion is binary (YES/NO) and specific to the prompt. Also, avoid generic advice. The criteria should be based on the structure and content of the reference and sample responses.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 다문화 가정의 사회 통합 과정에서의 어려움과 정부·지역사회 협력 정책 제안을 명확히 설명해야 합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"comprehensiveness_of_challenges\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 언어 장벽, 교육 격차, 고용 취약성, 사회적 차별 등 사회 통합 과정의 주요 어려움을 다각적으로 설명해야 합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"specificity_of_policies\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 정부와 지역사회가 공동으로 실행할 수 있는 구체적인 정책·프로그램(예: 언어 교육, 통합 지원센터)을 제안해야 합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"collaboration_between_actors\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 정부와 지역사회가 협력하여 문제를 해결할 수 있는 구조적 접근(예: 데이터 기반 정책, 지역사회 통합 프로그램)을 강조해야 합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"measurable_outcomes\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 정책의 성과를 평가할 수 있는 지표(예: 취업률, 한국어 수준, 차별 신고 처리 시간)를 제시해야 합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"logical_structure\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 어려움 분석 → 정책 제안 → 실행 로드맵 → 성과 지표 등 구조적으로 정리되어야 합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"cultural_sensitivity\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 다문화 가정의 문화적 배경과 정체성 존중을 위한 정책(예: 이중언어 지원, 문화 중개자 양성)을 포함해야 합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"practical_feasibility\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 현실적인 자원·시간·지역별 조건에 맞춘 실행 가능성(예: 농산어촌 이동형 서비스, 소규모 창업 지원)을 제안해야 합니다.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
