torm possible criteria:\n\n1. **Acknowledges lack of exact data** – Must state that exact figures aren't available.\n2. **Provides approximate ranges** – Gives numerical estimates with ranges.\n3. **Differentiates by gender** – Separates male and female literacy rates.\n4. **Specifies time periods** – Clearly defines the start and end of the 19th century.\n5. **Includes factors influencing literacy** – Mentions factors like school expansion, documents, etc.\n6. **Explains methodology** – Explains how the estimates are derived.\n7. **Handles regional disparities** – Acknowledges regional differences.\n8. **Considers definition of literacy** – Clarifies if it's basic reading or more advanced.\n\nNow, check if these are binary (yes/no) and specific. The reference response doesn't provide numbers, so the criteria should check for those elements. Also, the samples include some of these elements, so the criteria should align with that.\n\nNeed to make sure each criterion is prompt-specific. For example, \"specifies time periods\" is relevant here. Also, the response should not be generic, so each criterion must directly relate to the question's requirements.\n\nI think these 8 criteria cover the necessary aspects. Now, structure them into JSON with the required fields.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 '정확한 데이터 없음'을 인정하고 추정 범위를 제시해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"methodological_clarity\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 추정 방법(예: 서당 확산, 문서 서명률 등)을 설명해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"gender_distinction\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 남성과 여성의 문해율 차이를 구분해 추정해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"temporal_specification\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 '19세기 초'와 '19세기 말'을 구체적으로 구분해 추정해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"factor_inclusion\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 사설 서당 확산, 한글 보급 등 영향 요인을 언급해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"regional_disparity\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 도시/농촌, 지역 간 격차를 설명해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"definition_clarity\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 '기초 문해' vs '한문 독해' 등의 정의 차이를 명시해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"numerical_range\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 문해율 증가폭을 수치 범위(예: +10–15%p)로 제시해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
