{"prompt_id": "prompt_7db5627ebdc8", "pair_id": "pair_55395348738c", "method": "rrd_pairwise_reference", "generator_family": "qwen_small", "generator_model": "Qwen/Qwen3-4B-FP8", "criteria": [{"id": "F1", "axis": "instruction_following", "importance": "essential", "weight": 0.2941176470588235, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 사용자 요청을 직접적이고 빠짐없이 수행한다. [smoke:2e3d73]", "self_contained": true}, {"id": "F2", "axis": "correctness", "importance": "essential", "weight": 0.2941176470588235, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 사실 오류와 근거 없는 단정을 피하고 정확한 내용을 제공한다. [smoke:e7ef60]", "self_contained": true}, {"id": "F3", "axis": "completeness", "importance": "important", "weight": 0.20588235294117643, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 핵심 요소를 누락하지 않고 필요한 설명을 포함한다. [smoke:a35747]", "self_contained": true}, {"id": "F4", "axis": "korean_naturalness", "importance": "important", "weight": 0.20588235294117643, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 자연스럽고 읽기 쉬운 한국어 문장을 사용한다. [smoke:8ce5a4]", "self_contained": true}], "rar_items": [], "generation_metadata": {"fallback_used": "rrd_static_fallback", "errors": ["'\"satisfied\"'"], "auxiliary_sample_ids": ["sample_01", "sample_02", "sample_03", "sample_04", "sample_05", "sample_06", "sample_07", "sample_08"], "reference_guidance_used": true, "raw_output": "<think>\nOkay, I need to create a JSON with 8 criteria for evaluating the responses to the user's query about Korea's low birth rate problem. The user provided a reference response and several sample responses. The criteria should be specific to the prompt, binary (YES/NO), and not vague.\n\nFirst, I'll look at the reference response. It has sections on current situation, causes, and policy proposals. The sample responses also follow a similar structure but with more detailed data and specific policies.\n\nThe main elements in the reference and samples are: current situation analysis, cause analysis, policy proposals, and specific policies like economic support, social awareness, workplace flexibility, etc.\n\nSo, the criteria should cover aspects like following the instruction, providing a comprehensive analysis, including specific policies, using data, addressing both economic and social factors, ensuring feasibility, and having a clear structure.\n\nLet me list possible criteria:\n\n1. Instruction Following: Does the response address all parts of the query (analysis of current situation, causes, and policy proposals)?\n2. Comprehensive Analysis: Does it cover all key aspects (current situation, causes, policies)?\n3. Specific Policies: Are the proposed policies detailed and actionable?\n4. Data Usage: Does it include specific data or statistics?\n5. Economic and Social Factors: Does it address both economic and social causes?\n6. Feasibility: Are the policies realistic and implementable?\n7. Clear Structure: Is the response well-organized with clear sections?\n8. Originality: Are the policies innovative and not just standard ones?\n\nNow, I need to make sure each criterion is binary (YES/NO) and specific. Let me check if these fit.\n\nFor example, \"Instruction Following\" would check if the response includes all required parts. \"Comprehensive Analysis\" would check if all key aspects are covered. \"Specific Policies\" would check if policies are detailed. \"Data Usage\" checks if data is included. \"Economic and Social Factors\" checks if both are addressed. \"Feasibility\" checks if policies are realistic. \"Clear Structure\" checks if the response is well-organized. \"Originality\" checks if policies are innovative.\n\nI need to ensure that each criterion is prompt-specific. The user's prompt asks for analysis of current situation, causes, and policy proposals. So the criteria should align with these elements.\n\nNow, I'll structure the JSON with these criteria, making sure each has an ID, axis, importance, weight, text in Korean, and self-contained as true.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 저출산 현황, 원인 분석, 혁신적 정책 제안을 모두 포함하고 있는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"comprehensive_analysis\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 저출산의 경제적, 사회적, 구조적 원인을 다각도로 분석하고 있는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"specific_policies\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 실행 가능한 구체적인 정책 제안을 포함하고 있는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"data_usage\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 통계 또는 실증적 데이터를 기반으로 분석하고 있는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"feasibility\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답의 제안 정책이 현실적으로 실행 가능한가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"structure_clarity\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 논리적 구조가 명확하고 분석·제안이 구분되어 있는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"innovation\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답의 정책 제안이 혁신적이고 기존 정책과 차별화된가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"originality\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답의 정책 제안이 독창적이고 실용적인가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
