fic industries)\n- Balanced regional development (e.g., infrastructure, social services)\n- Decentralization (e.g., local autonomy, financial autonomy)\n- Policy frameworks (e.g., block grants, regulatory sandboxes)\n- Implementation strategies (e.g., public procurement, innovation hubs)\n- Sustainability (e.g., green transition, carbon reduction)\n- Inclusivity (e.g., talent attraction, social services)\n- Data and governance (e.g., KPIs, data platforms)\n\nNow, I need to translate these into 8 binary criteria. Each should be specific to the prompt and not generic. Let me list possible criteria:\n\n1. **Instruction Following**: Does the response address all three aspects (specialization, balance, decentralization)?\n2. **Regional Specialization**: Does it propose specific industries or clusters?\n3. **Balanced Development**: Does it include strategies for equitable development across regions?\n4. **Decentralization**: Does it suggest local autonomy or financial independence?\n5. **Policy Frameworks**: Does it mention specific policies like block grants or regulatory sandboxes?\n6. **Implementation Strategies**: Does it include actionable steps like public procurement or innovation hubs?\n7. **Sustainability**: Does it address green transition or carbon reduction?\n8. **Inclusivity and Governance**: Does it cover talent attraction, social services, and data governance?\n\nI need to ensure each criterion is binary and specific. Let me check if these are covered in the samples. The reference and samples do mention these elements. Now, I'll structure them into JSON with the required fields.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 지역 특화 산업, 지역 간 균형 발전, 지방 분권 강화의 세 가지 주요 방안을 모두 포함하고 있는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"regional_specialization\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 구체적인 지역별 산업 특화 전략(예: 부산 해양에너지, 울산 수소)을 제시하고 있는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"balanced_development\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 지역 간 인프라·교육·의료 접근성 개선을 위한 균형 발전 전략을 포함하고 있는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"decentralization\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 지방 재정 자율성 강화(예: 블록그랜트, 지방세 확충) 또는 규제 권한 이양을 제안하고 있는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"policy_frameworks\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 규제 샌드박스, 공공조달 지역가점, 데이터 플랫폼 등 구체적인 정책 도구를 제안하고 있는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"implementation_strategies\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 지역 특화 산업의 초기 시범(예: 수소 밸류체인) 또는 인프라 리모델링을 위한 실행 계획을 포함하고 있는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"sustainability\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 녹색 전환(예: 재생에너지, 탄소 감축) 또는 지역 수익 모델 연계를 위한 전략을 제시하고 있는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"inclusivity_governance\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 청년 유입, 지역 인재 정착, 주민 참여 예산 등 사회적 포용성과 데이터 기반 거버넌스를 포함하고 있는가?\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
