n Yeon and Song Gikhyeuk, and the overall narrative structure.\n\nThe criteria need to be specific, binary (yes/no), and not vague. Let's start with instruction following. The response must include the TV scene and the interrogation. So, R1 could be about including both elements.\n\nNext, the storyline must follow the given plot points. R2 could check if the TV explanation and interrogation are present.\n\nThen, character consistency. The samples have characters like Zheng Mingseon, Song Gikhyeuk, and Tock Myeongseon. R3 could verify that all main characters are included.\n\nTension and conflict are important. The samples show conflict between Information Yeon and Song Gikhyeuk. R4 could check if this conflict is present.\n\nNarrative structure: The response should have a beginning (TV), middle (interrogation), and end (conclusion). R5 could assess if the structure is clear.\n\nLanguage style: The reference and samples use a novel style with descriptive language. R6 could check if the language is appropriate.\n\nPacing and flow: The samples have a tight, concise flow. R7 could ensure the response is concise and flows well.\n\nOriginality: The samples avoid clichés. R8 could check if the response is original and not repetitive.\n\nWait, the user said 8 criteria. Let me make sure each is specific and binary. Also, avoid generic advice. Let me list them again:\n\n1. Instruction Following: Includes both TV explanation and interrogation scene.\n2. Storyline Accuracy: Correctly follows the given plot points.\n3. Character Consistency: All main characters are present.\n4. Tension and Conflict: Shows conflict between Information Yeon and Song Gikhyeuk.\n5. Narrative Structure: Clear beginning, middle, end.\n6. Language Style: Uses novel-style descriptive language.\n7. Pacing and Flow: Concise and well-structured.\n8. Originality: Avoids clichés and is original.\n\nYes, that's 8. Now, translate these into Korean, assign IDs, importance, weights, etc. Make sure each is binary and specific.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"TV에서 매국노에 대한 설명과 취조실 대화가 모두 포함되어야 한다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"storyline_accuracy\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"정보연과 송기혁의 심문, 정명선과의 대화, TV 해설의 연관성 유지해야 한다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"character_consistency\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"정명선, 송기혁, 정보연, 탁명선 등 주요 인물의 행동과 대화가 일관되어야 한다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"tension_and_conflict\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"정보연과 송기혁의 갈등, 탁명선의 위험성에 대한 긴장감이 표현되어야 한다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"narrative_structure\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"TV 설명 → 취조실 대화 → 갈등의 전개가 명확하게 구조화되어야 한다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"language_style\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.1,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"소설 형식의 묘사어휘(예: '희미한 불빛', '냉기')가 사용되어야 한다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"pacing_and_flow\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.1,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"300자 내외로 짧고 밀집된 서사가 흐르고 있어야 한다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"originality\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.1,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"일반적인 표현이나 촉각을 피하고 독특한 서사가 포함되어야 한다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
