 at the sample responses, they all touch on similar points: the phonetic similarity of 4 to 'death', cultural practices of avoiding 4, the significance of 7 in Western traditions, and the Seven Stars in East Asian culture. They also mention the influence of modern media on the perception of 7.\n\nSo, the key elements to include in the criteria are:\n\n1. Whether the response explains the phonetic similarity of 4 to 'death' in East Asian languages.\n2. Whether the response mentions cultural practices of avoiding 4 (like not using 4 in building floors, hotel rooms).\n3. Whether the response discusses the historical example of Emperor Charles IV's obsession with 4.\n4. Whether the response explains the significance of 7 in Western traditions (like the Seven Days, Seven Colors).\n5. Whether the response mentions the Seven Stars (칠성) in East Asian traditions.\n6. Whether the response contrasts the cultural differences between East and West regarding 4 and 7.\n7. Whether the response includes examples of how these beliefs affect daily life (like avoiding 4 in phone numbers).\n8. Whether the response acknowledges that these are cultural practices, not scientific facts.\n\nEach criterion should be a binary yes/no check. I need to make sure they are specific to the prompt and not generic. Let me structure them accordingly.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 4가 '사(死)'와 발음이 같아 불길함을 연상시킨 언어적 이유를 설명합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 4를 회피하는 문화적 관습(층수, 객실 번호 생략 등)을 언급합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 서구 문화에서 7의 '완전성' 상징(7일 창조, 7색 무지개)을 설명합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 동아시아 전통에서 7의 '칠성 신앙'과 '칠석' 민속을 언급합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 4와 7의 문화적 차이(동아시아 vs 서구)를 비교 설명합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 현대 문화(777 슬롯머신, 카지노)에서 7의 행운 상징이 확산된 사례를 언급합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 숫자 길흉이 문화적 관습임을 명시하고, 과학적 근거가 없다는 점을 설명합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 4와 7의 상징이 세대·상황에 따라 달라질 수 있음을 강조합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
