user's needs. Each criterion should be specific and binary. Let me brainstorm possible criteria:\n\n1. **Instruction Following**: Does the response address all parts of the user's question (apps, stock cycles, account tips)?\n2. **App Recommendations**: Are specific apps listed with their features?\n3. **Stock Price Cycles Explanation**: Does it clarify that there's no fixed cycle and mention factors affecting prices?\n4. **Account Opening Tips**: Are practical tips provided for opening an account?\n5. **Currency Conversion Details**: Does it mention exchange rates and fees for foreign stocks?\n6. **Risk Management Advice**: Are there tips on managing risks like DCA or stop-loss?\n7. **Tax Information**: Does it cover tax implications for domestic and foreign stocks?\n8. **User-Friendly Language**: Is the language simple and easy to understand for a beginner?\n\nWait, the user is a beginner, so the language should be simple. Also, the reference response includes detailed explanations of stock cycles, which is important. Let me check if these criteria are specific enough and binary. For example, \"App Recommendations\" can be a YES if specific apps are listed with their features. \"Stock Price Cycles Explanation\" would be YES if it clarifies there's no fixed cycle and explains factors. \n\nI need to make sure each criterion is specific to the prompt and not generic. Also, avoid vague advice. Let me adjust the criteria to be more precise. Maybe:\n\n1. **Instruction Following**: Covers all three parts of the query.\n2. **App Recommendations**: Lists specific apps with their features.\n3. **Stock Cycle Explanation**: Explains that there's no fixed cycle and mentions factors.\n4. **Account Tips**: Provides practical tips for account setup.\n5. **Currency Conversion**: Details on exchange rates and fees for foreign stocks.\n6. **Risk Management**: Includes advice on DCA, stop-loss, etc.\n7. **Tax Information**: Covers tax implications for domestic and foreign stocks.\n8. **User-Friendly Language**: Uses simple, clear language for beginners.\n\nYes, these seem specific and binary. Now, I need to translate these into Korean, assign IDs, importance, weights, and ensure they are binary. The reference response includes all these elements, so the criteria should be based on whether the response includes these aspects.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 주식 투자 앱 추천, 주가 변동 주기 설명, 증권계좌 개설 팁을 모두 포함합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"specific_app_recommendations\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 토스증권, 카카오페이증권, 키움증권 등 구체적인 앱을 명시하고 그 특징을 설명합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"stock_cycle_explanation\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 주가 변동 주기의 정해진 패턴이 없음을 명확히 설명하고, 실적, 금리, 뉴스 등 영향 요인을 언급합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"account_setup_tips\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 비대면 계좌 개설 절차, 수수료 비교, 환전우대 이벤트, 보안 설정 등 실용적인 개설 팁을 제공합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"currency_conversion_details\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 해외주식 환전 스프레드, 자동환전 설정, 환전우대 이벤트 등 금융 거래 관련 세부 사항을 설명합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"risk_management_advice\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 분할매수, 손절 기준 설정, 리스크 관리 전략 등 투자 위험 완화 방법을 제시합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"tax_information\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 국내외 주식의 세금 정책(양도소득세, 배당소득세)을 명확히 설명하고, 세액공제 방법을 언급합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"user_friendly_language\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 초보자에게 쉬운 언어로 설명하며, 복잡한 용어를 피하고 실용적인 팁을 중심으로 구성합니다.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
