instruction, but some include more detailed advice, like ORS recipes, specific drink combinations, and even step-by-step instructions. The reference response is concise but covers all necessary points.\n\nNow, I need to identify 8 criteria. Let's think about what's essential. The main aspects are:\n\n1. Instruction Followed: Only drinks, no solid food.\n2. Soft and Easy to Consume: Foods and drinks that are soft.\n3. Explanation of Benefits: Why each item is recommended.\n4. Practical Tips: How to consume them (e.g., temperature, portion size).\n5. Avoidance of Harmful Items: What to avoid.\n6. Clear Structure: Organized into categories like drinks, foods, etc.\n7. Specificity: Detailed examples rather than vague suggestions.\n8. Health Considerations: Mentioning hydration, electrolytes, or other health aspects.\n\nWait, the user said to avoid vague advice. So, each criterion should be specific. Let me check the reference again. The reference includes specific items like banana, yogurt, coconut water, etc., with explanations. The samples also have similar specifics.\n\nSo, the criteria should be:\n\n1. Instruction Followed (Only drinks, no solid food)\n2. Soft and Easy to Consume (Soft foods and drinks)\n3. Explanation of Benefits (Why each item is recommended)\n4. Practical Tips (How to consume, like temperature, portion)\n5. Avoidance of Harmful Items (What to avoid)\n6. Clear Structure (Organized into categories)\n7. Specific Examples (Detailed items, not vague)\n8. Health Considerations (Hydration, electrolytes, etc.)\n\nNow, translating these into Korean and ensuring they are binary. For example, \"Instruction Followed\" would be a yes if the response only includes drinks. \"Soft and Easy to Consume\" would be yes if the items are soft. Each criterion must be specific and not generic.\n\nI need to make sure each criterion is prompt-specific. The user's query is about post-drinking, soft foods and drinks. So, the rubric should focus on that context.\n\nLet me check if these criteria are covered in the samples. The reference response includes all these, and the samples also have similar points. So, the 8 criteria should be based on these aspects.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 숙취 해소를 위한 음료만 추천하고, 고기나 단단한 음식을 포함하지 않음\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"soft_eating_compatibility\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"추천 음료는 부드럽고 위에 부담이 적은 성분을 포함함\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"benefit_explanation\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"각 음료의 숙취 해소 효과나 건강적 장점이 명확히 설명됨\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"practical_consumption_tips\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"음료 섭취 방법(온도, 양, 빈도 등)에 대한 구체적 조언 제공\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"avoidance_guidance\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"위 자극이나 탈수를 유발하는 음료(커피, 탄산 등)를 피해야 하는 이유 명시됨\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"structure_organization\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답이 음료, 피해야 할 것, 섭취 요령 등 구조적으로 분류됨\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"specific_examples\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"구체적인 음료 예시(예: 코코넛워터, 생강차)가 포함됨\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"health_consideration\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"수분 보충, 전해질 균형, 간 보호 등 건강 관련 요소가 언급됨\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
