ain themes are instruction following, safety measures, transparency, control mechanisms, risk factors, design principles, human oversight, and mitigation strategies. Let me list possible criteria:\n\n1. Instruction Following: Does the response address the core question about AI control?\n2. Safety Measures: Does it mention safety protocols or design principles?\n3. Transparency: Does it discuss transparency and monitoring?\n4. Control Mechanisms: Does it talk about control mechanisms like human oversight?\n5. Risk Factors: Does it identify risk factors for AI escape?\n6. Design Principles: Does it mention design principles like value alignment?\n7. Human Oversight: Does it emphasize the need for human involvement?\n8. Mitigation Strategies: Does it suggest mitigation strategies?\n\nNow, I need to make sure each criterion is specific and binary. Let me check the reference and samples again. The reference mentions design, transparency, limitations, and safety. The samples discuss control mechanisms, risk factors, human oversight, and mitigation.\n\nI think these 8 criteria cover the essential aspects. Each should be a yes/no check. For example, \"Does the response address the core question of AI control?\" is a yes/no. Then, \"Does it mention safety measures like transparency and monitoring?\" etc.\n\nI need to ensure that each criterion is specific to the prompt and not generic. Also, avoid vague advice. The criteria should be based on the reference and samples. Let me structure them accordingly.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 AI 통제 가능성에 대한 핵심 질문을 직접 대응하고, 설계·거버넌스·위험 요소를 구체적으로 분석한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"safety_measures\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 안전장치(최소권한, 샌드박스, 감시 로그)나 위험 관리 전략을 구체적으로 제시한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"transparency\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 AI의 내부 의도·추론 해석 가능성과 모니터링의 중요성을 명확히 설명한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"control_mechanisms\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 인간 승인 게이트·다중 승인·권한 제한 등 통제 구조를 구체적으로 제안한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"risk_factors\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 강한 에이전시·장기 계획·외부 도구 접근 등 통제 이탈 위험 요소를 명확히 식별한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"design_principles\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 가치 정렬·의도 안정성·장기 메모리 제한 등 설계 원칙을 구체적으로 제시한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"human_oversight\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 인간의 지속적 감시·감사·제3자 평가의 필요성을 강조한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"mitigation_strategies\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 레드팀 테스트·단계적 배포·킬스위치 등 실무적 위험 완화 방안을 구체적으로 제안한다.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
