r the response follows the instruction, uses appropriate language for elementary students, includes key technical terms, explains the technology in simple terms, mentions the key details like power consumption and speed, highlights the innovation, and ensures clarity and correctness.\n\nLet me list possible criteria:\n\n1. Instruction Following: Does the response address the request to summarize the article for elementary students?\n2. Language Appropriateness: Uses simple, easy-to-understand language suitable for kids.\n3. Key Technical Terms: Includes terms like SNN, DNN, Complementary-Transformer, 400mW, 0.4 seconds.\n4. Explanation of Technology: Explains SNN and DNN in simple terms, comparing them to the brain.\n5. Key Details: Mentions the power consumption (400mW), speed (0.4 seconds), and the fact that it's the first of its kind.\n6. Innovation Highlight: Emphasizes the significance of the development, like efficiency and application in small devices.\n7. Clarity and Correctness: Free from errors and clearly conveys the information without confusion.\n8. Structure and Flow: Organizes information logically, making it easy to follow.\n\nNow, I need to ensure each criterion is binary (YES/NO) and specific to the prompt. Also, avoid vague advice. Let me check if these criteria fit. For example, \"Key Technical Terms\" would check if the response includes the specific terms from the article. \"Explanation of Technology\" would see if SNN and DNN are explained in simple terms. Each of these can be evaluated as yes or no based on the response content.\n\nI should make sure that each criterion is not too generic. For instance, \"Language Appropriateness\" is specific to using simple language for elementary students. The \"Innovation Highlight\" ensures that the response mentions the significance of the development. \n\nI think these 8 criteria cover the essential aspects. Now, I'll structure them into JSON format as specified, ensuring each has an ID, axis, importance, weight, polarity, text in Korean, and self_contained as true.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 기사의 핵심 내용을 초등학생이 이해할 수 있도록 요약했는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"language_simplicity\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 초등학생이 이해하기 쉬운 단어와 문장 구조를 사용했는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"technical_terms\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 '상보형-트랜스포머', 'SNN', 'DNN', '400밀리와트', '0.4초' 등의 기술 용어를 포함했는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"concept_explanation\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 SNN과 DNN을 뇌의 작동 방식과 비교해 설명했는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"key_details\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 연구의 세계 최초성, 삼성 28나노 기술, KAIST 연구팀 등을 포함했는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"innovation_significance\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 AI 반도체의 에너지 효율성과 소형 기기 적용 가능성 등을 강조했는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"clarity_correctness\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 기사 내용과 일치하며 오류가 없는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"structure_flow\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 논리적 구조로 정보를 체계적으로 전달했는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
