hould focus on what's essential for high-end dining, not generic advice. Let me think about the key elements that distinguish high-quality responses in this context.\n\n1. **Instruction Following**: Does the response directly address the task of transforming street food into high-end dining? The reference and samples all do this, so this is essential.\n\n2. **Innovative Techniques**: Use of advanced cooking methods or creative presentations. The samples mention things like \"clear consome,\" \"fermentation,\" and \"texture contrast.\"\n\n3. **Ingredient Quality and Source**: Mentioning premium or local ingredients, like \"seasonal produce\" or \"local seafood.\" The samples emphasize using local and seasonal ingredients.\n\n4. **Texture Contrast**: Creating a balance of textures (crunchy, soft, creamy). The samples discuss various textures in detail.\n\n5. **Presentation and Aesthetics**: How the dishes are plated and presented. The samples describe detailed plating techniques and use of materials like \"white porcelain.\"\n\n6. **Service and Storytelling**: Including elements that tell a story or enhance the dining experience, like \"tableside performances\" or \"local stories.\"\n\n7. **Sustainability and Ethics**: Using sustainable practices or ethical sourcing. The samples mention reducing waste and using local, seasonal ingredients.\n\n8. **Flavor Complexity and Balance**: Ensuring the dishes have a balanced and complex flavor profile. The samples discuss flavor layers and balance.\n\nNow, I need to make sure each criterion is specific, binary, and not too vague. Let me check if these criteria cover the key aspects from the reference and samples. Yes, they do. Each criterion is a yes/no check based on the presence of specific elements in the response.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 한국 길거리 음식을 고급 식당에서 제공할 수 있는 창의적인 방법을 구체적으로 제안합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"innovative_techniques\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 저온 조리, 클리어 콘소메, 퓨레/젤/폼 등 고급 기술을 활용해 길거리 음식을 재해석합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"ingredient_quality\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 제철 재료, 지역산 해산물, 숙성 장(간장·고추장) 등을 통해 재료의 품질을 강조합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"texture_contrast\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 바삭–쫀득–크리미 등 다양한 질감을 조화롭게 결합해 길거리의 특성을 고급화합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"presentation_aesthetics\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 백자 그릇, 온돌 스톤 플레이트, 미니멀리즘 스타일로 미학적인 플레이팅을 제안합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"service_storytelling\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 테이블사이드 마무리, 지역 스토리 카드, 포장마차 카트 연출로 경험을 강화합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"sustainability_ethics\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.1,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 부산물 재활용, 지역산 재료 사용, 채식 대안을 통해 지속가능성을 강조합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"flavor_complexity\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.1,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 고추장-간장-멸치육수의 향기 조화, 소스 레이어링으로 맛의 밀도를 높입니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
