 has a clear setting, named characters, and a logical flow of dialogue. The sample responses also have similar elements but vary in how they structure the dialogue and the depth of the content.\n\nThe criteria should be binary (yes/no) and specific. Let me brainstorm possible criteria:\n\n1. Instruction Following: Does the response follow the user's request to write a script of a dialogue between Joseon scholars?\n2. Historical Accuracy: Are the characters and their historical context accurately represented?\n3. Character Consistency: Do the characters maintain their roles and personalities throughout the dialogue?\n4. Dialogue Flow: Is the conversation logical and coherent, with each character's lines responding appropriately?\n5. Setting Description: Does the response include a detailed and appropriate setting for the dialogue?\n6. Use of Specific Elements: Does the response include elements like the characters' names, their historical roles, and the context of their discussion?\n7. Depth of Content: Does the dialogue address the themes of realism and practicality as per the reference?\n8. Coherence and Structure: Is the script well-structured with clear scenes and transitions?\n\nWait, some of these might be overlapping. Let me check if they are distinct enough. For example, \"Historical Accuracy\" and \"Use of Specific Elements\" might be related. Maybe I can adjust to ensure each criterion is unique and specific to the task.\n\nAnother angle: the reference response includes a specific setting, named characters, and a structured dialogue. The samples vary in these aspects. So, the criteria should check for these elements.\n\nLet me finalize the 8 criteria:\n\n1. Instruction Following: Does the response create a script of a dialogue between Joseon scholars as requested?\n2. Character Consistency: Are the characters' roles and personalities consistent throughout the dialogue?\n3. Setting Description: Does the response include a detailed and appropriate setting for the dialogue?\n4. Dialogue Flow: Is the conversation logically structured with appropriate responses between characters?\n5. Historical Accuracy: Are the characters and their historical context accurately represented?\n6. Use of Specific Elements: Does the response include elements like the characters' names, their historical roles, and the context of their discussion?\n7. Depth of Content: Does the dialogue address the themes of realism and practicality as per the reference?\n8. Coherence and Structure: Is the script well-structured with clear scenes and transitions?\n\nI need to make sure each criterion is binary and specific. Also, avoid generic advice. Now, translate these into Korean with the required JSON structure.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 조선 시대 실학자들의 대화를 스크립트 형태로 작성하는 요청을 충실히 따르는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"character_consistency\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"각 인물의 역할과 성격이 대화 중 일관되게 유지되는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"setting_description\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"대화의 배경(장소, 시간, 분위기)이 구체적이고 적절하게 묘사되는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"dialogue_flow\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"대화가 논리적이고 자연스럽게 흐르며, 각 인물의 대화가 상호작용을 반영하는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"historical_accuracy\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"인물의 역사적 배경과 역할이 정확하게 반영되는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"specific_elements\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"인물 이름, 역사적 맥락, 대화 주제 등 구체적 요소가 포함되는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"depth_of_content\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"대화가 실학의 실용성과 현실적 문제 해결을 다루는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"coherence_structure\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"스크립트가 구조적으로 명확하고 장면 전환, 대화 흐름이 자연스럽게 이어지는가?\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
