.\n\nLooking at the reference response, it follows the user's instruction by providing a list of ingredients and marketing strategies. The samples go deeper into product formats, cultural aspects, and health benefits. So, the criteria should reflect these elements.\n\nI need to make sure each criterion is binary (YES/NO) and specific to the prompt. Let's brainstorm possible criteria:\n\n1. **Instruction Following**: Does the response accurately follow the user's request to list Korean ingredients and suggest marketing ideas?\n2. **Global Relevance**: Are the ingredients and strategies suitable for global markets?\n3. **Product Format Innovation**: Does the response suggest innovative product formats?\n4. **Cultural Storytelling**: Does it incorporate cultural or regional stories?\n5. **Health Benefits**: Does it highlight health aspects like low sodium, gluten-free, etc.?\n6. **Ease of Use**: Are the products easy to use and integrate into everyday cooking?\n7. **Unique Selling Points**: Does it present unique features that differentiate the ingredients?\n8. **Marketability**: Are the marketing ideas practical and appealing to a global audience?\n\nNow, I need to ensure these are specific and binary. For example, \"Cultural Storytelling\" would check if the response includes stories about the origin or traditional uses of the ingredients. \"Health Benefits\" would check if it mentions low sodium, gluten-free, etc.\n\nI should also avoid generic advice and focus on the specific aspects mentioned in the reference and samples. Each criterion should be tied directly to the user's request and the quality of the response.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 한국 재료 목록 작성과 마케팅 아이디어 제안을 완전히 수행했는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"global_relevance\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"재료와 마케팅 아이디어가 글로벌 시장에서 효과적일 수 있는지?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"product_format_innovation\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"재료별 제품 포맷(예: 스퀴즈, 티백, 스낵)이 혁신적이고 사용자 친화적일 수 있는지?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"cultural_storytelling\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"재료의 원산지, 전통, 제조법 등 한국 문화적 스토리가 포함되었는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"health_benefits\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"건강 기능성(예: 저염, 글루텐프리, 비건)이 명확히 제안되었는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"ease_of_use\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"재료와 마케팅 아이디어가 사용자에게 쉽게 적용 가능한지?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"unique_selling_points\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"재료의 독특한 차별화 포인트(예: 천연 감칠맛, 발효 기술)가 명확히 제안되었는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"marketability\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"마케팅 아이디어가 실제 구매 행동을 유도할 수 있는지?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
