s, suggesting solutions, ensuring the solutions are institutional and cultural, addressing both gender and intersectional issues, and ensuring the response is comprehensive and well-structured.\n\nNow, I need to translate these into 8 specific criteria. Let's start with instruction following. The response must address all parts of the query: current state, causes, and solutions. Next, data on current issues like income disparity and employment. Then, analysis of causes such as labor market structure and cultural norms. Solutions should include institutional and cultural changes. Also, addressing intersectional issues like overlapping inequalities. Ensuring the response is comprehensive and well-structured. Finally, the use of specific examples and data.\n\nWait, the user said to avoid generic advice and focus on the prompt-specific aspects. So each criterion should check if the response meets a specific part of the query. Let me list them:\n\n1. Instruction Following: Does the response address all parts of the query (current state, causes, solutions)?\n2. Data on Current Issues: Does it include specific data on income disparity, employment, etc.?\n3. Cause Analysis: Does it analyze structural and cultural causes?\n4. Institutional Solutions: Does it propose institutional changes?\n5. Cultural Solutions: Does it suggest cultural changes?\n6. Intersectional Consideration: Does it address overlapping inequalities?\n7. Comprehensive Coverage: Does it cover all aspects of the query?\n8. Specific Examples: Does it use specific examples or data?\n\nNow, I need to make sure each criterion is binary and specific. Let me check the samples. The reference and samples include detailed data, analysis of causes, both institutional and cultural solutions, intersectional issues, and comprehensive coverage. So these criteria should work.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 '실태 분석', '원인 분석', '해소 방안'을 모두 포함하고 있는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"data_inclusion\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"실태 분석에 OECD 기준 임금 격차, 여성 고용률, 돌봄 시간 등 구체적 데이터를 포함하고 있는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"cause_analysis\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"구조적 원인(노동시장 이중구조, 성별 역할 고착 등)을 명확히 분석하고 있는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"institutional_solutions\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"제도적 변화(임금 투명성, 돌봄 인프라 확충 등)를 구체적인 제안으로 포함하고 있는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"cultural_solutions\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"문화적 변화(남성 돌봄 참여 촉진, 성평등 교육 등)를 실천 가능한 방안으로 제시하고 있는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"intersectionality\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"이주여성, 장애 여성 등 교차적 불평등을 고려한 해결 방안을 포함하고 있는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"comprehensiveness\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"실행 로드맵과 성과 지표(임금 격차 축소, 여성 리더십 비율 등)를 구체적으로 제시하고 있는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"specific_examples\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"실제 사례(상장사 이사 성별 비율, 디지털 성범죄 대응 체계 등)를 구체적으로 언급하고 있는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
