ive, use of poetic devices like imagery and metaphor, emotional depth, coherence, structure, originality, and adherence to the theme.\n\nSo, the criteria should be specific and binary. Let me think of 8 criteria. \n\n1. Instruction Following: Does the response use the given poems as motifs?\n2. Narrative Coherence: Is there a clear, logical story flow?\n3. Poetic Devices: Use of imagery, metaphor, etc.\n4. Emotional Depth: Does it convey genuine emotions?\n5. Thematic Adherence: Does it stick to the theme of dreams and hope?\n6. Structural Integrity: Proper poem structure (stanzas, rhythm)\n7. Originality: Unique ideas not just rephrasing the reference\n8. Language Quality: Use of vivid, precise language\n\nWait, but the user said to avoid generic advice. So maybe instead of \"language quality,\" focus on specific aspects like use of poetic devices. Also, each criterion must be binary (yes/no) and specific to the prompt.\n\nLet me refine:\n\n1. Instruction Following: Uses \"Sesik\" and \"Bol Heunyeong Bap\" as motifs.\n2. Narrative Flow: Clear, logical progression of the story.\n3. Poetic Imagery: Effective use of vivid imagery.\n4. Emotional Resonance: Conveys genuine emotions related to dreams and hope.\n5. Thematic Focus: Strong emphasis on dreams and hope.\n6. Structural Coherence: Proper poem structure (stanzas, rhythm).\n7. Originality: Unique perspective or original ideas.\n8. Language Precision: Use of precise, evocative language.\n\nYes, these seem specific and binary. Now, I need to make sure each is a yes/no and not vague. Also, the criteria should be in Korean as per the example. Let me check the example again. The example has criteria like \"instruction_following\" with a text in Korean. So I need to translate these criteria into Korean, ensuring they are specific and not generic.\n\nFinal check: Each criterion is prompt-specific, binary, and not generic. The reference and samples should be used to guide the criteria, not copied. The JSON structure should have 8 criteria with the required fields.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 '서시'와 '별 헤는 밤'을 모티프로 한 시적 이야기를 구체적으로 반영한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"narrative_flow\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"시는 청년의 꿈과 희망의 여정을 명확한 서사 구조로 전개한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"poetic_imagination\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"시는 이미지, 은유, 비유 등 시적 창의성을 통해 감정을 시각화한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"emotional_resonance\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"시는 청년의 내면적 갈등과 희망의 갈등을 진정한 감정으로 전달한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"thematic_focus\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"시는 꿈과 희망의 청년 여정을 '서시'와 '별 헤는 밤'의 테마와 연결시킨다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"structural_coherence\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"시는 시적 구조(절, 리듬, 형식)를 일관되게 유지한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"originality\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"시는 기존의 시적 테마를 새로운 시각으로 재해석한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"language_precision\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"시는 정확하고 생동감 있는 언어를 통해 청년의 내면을 구체적으로 묘사한다.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
