: \n- Morphological complexity (morphological changes, affixes)\n- Honorific systems and politeness levels\n- Flexible word order and omission\n- Tokenization and subword unit issues\n- Code-switching and mixed scripts\n- Data scarcity and benchmark limitations\n- Contextual understanding and discourse coherence\n- Cultural and social norms in language use\n\nNow, I need to translate these into 8 specific, binary criteria. Let me list them out:\n\n1. **Morphological Complexity**: Does the response address the challenges of Korean's morphological complexity, including affixes and morphological changes?\n2. **Honorific Systems**: Does the response discuss the importance of honorific systems and politeness levels in Korean NLP?\n3. **Flexible Word Order**: Does the response mention the flexibility of Korean word order and the challenges of omitting subjects/objects?\n4. **Tokenization Challenges**: Does the response address the difficulties in tokenizing Korean text, including subword units and morphological boundaries?\n5. **Code-Switching and Mixed Scripts**: Does the response cover the issues of code-switching and mixed scripts in Korean NLP?\n6. **Data Scarcity and Benchmark Limitations**: Does the response discuss the lack of large-scale, high-quality Korean datasets and the limitations of existing benchmarks?\n7. **Contextual Understanding and Discourse Coherence**: Does the response emphasize the need for contextual understanding and discourse coherence in Korean NLP?\n8. **Cultural and Social Norms**: Does the response address the importance of cultural and social norms in Korean language processing?\n\nEach of these should be checked as YES or NO. Now, I need to make sure they are specific to the prompt and not generic. The prompt is about the challenges in Korean NLP and the importance of model development considering Korean characteristics. So these criteria should directly relate to that.\n\nI think these 8 points cover the main aspects discussed in the reference and samples. Now, I'll structure them into the JSON format as specified.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 한국어의 형태 변화, 조사 결합, 어미 변형 등 형태론적 복잡성을 정확히 인식하고 설명합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 한국어의 존댓말 체계, 공손도, 화행 등 사회언어학적 특성을 체계적으로 논의합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 한국어의 자유로운 어순, 주어 생략, 문맥 의존적 의미 해석을 핵심 난점으로 명시합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 토큰화의 어절 경계 불명확성, 조사/어미 결합 문제, 자모/음절 혼합 토크나이저 필요성을 설명합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 한국어와 영어/한자/이모지 혼용, 코드스위칭, 스크립트 변이 등 다중 언어/문자 체계의 난점을 다룹니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 대규모 한국어 데이터 부족, 벤치마크 범위 제한, 도메인 편향 문제를 핵심 개발 고려사항으로 제시합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 문맥 추론, 대화 맥락 유지, 생략 해소 등 문맥적 의미 파악의 중요성을 강조합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 한국어의 문화적 규범, 공손도 일관성, 사회적 관계 표현의 모델 설계에 대한 영향을 체계적으로 논의합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
