{"prompt_id": "prompt_8400ebeee547", "pair_id": "pair_8cbf69d8805f", "method": "rrd_pairwise_reference", "generator_family": "qwen_small", "generator_model": "Qwen/Qwen3-4B-FP8", "criteria": [{"id": "F1", "axis": "instruction_following", "importance": "essential", "weight": 0.2941176470588235, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 사용자 요청을 직접적이고 빠짐없이 수행한다. [smoke:37438b]", "self_contained": true}, {"id": "F2", "axis": "correctness", "importance": "essential", "weight": 0.2941176470588235, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 사실 오류와 근거 없는 단정을 피하고 정확한 내용을 제공한다. [smoke:aca1c1]", "self_contained": true}, {"id": "F3", "axis": "completeness", "importance": "important", "weight": 0.20588235294117643, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 핵심 요소를 누락하지 않고 필요한 설명을 포함한다. [smoke:41c474]", "self_contained": true}, {"id": "F4", "axis": "korean_naturalness", "importance": "important", "weight": 0.20588235294117643, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 자연스럽고 읽기 쉬운 한국어 문장을 사용한다. [smoke:198323]", "self_contained": true}], "rar_items": [], "generation_metadata": {"fallback_used": "rrd_static_fallback", "errors": ["'\"satisfied\"'"], "auxiliary_sample_ids": ["sample_01", "sample_02", "sample_03", "sample_04", "sample_05", "sample_06", "sample_07", "sample_08"], "reference_guidance_used": true, "raw_output": "<think>\nOkay, I need to create a JSON with 8 criteria for evaluating responses to the user's request about policy ideas for regional economic activation in South Korea. The user provided a reference response and several sample responses. The criteria must be specific to the prompt, binary (YES/NO), and not vague.\n\nFirst, I'll look at the user's prompt: \"제시해 보세요. 지역 특화 산업 육성, 지역 간 균형 발전, 지방 분권 강화 등의 방안을 고려해 보세요.\" So the main areas are regional specialization, balanced development between regions, and decentralization.\n\nLooking at the reference response, it has sections on each of these areas. The sample responses also cover these points in detail. Now, I need to identify key aspects that are essential for a good response.\n\nFirst criterion: Does the response follow the instruction? The user asked for policy ideas considering the three areas. So checking if the response addresses all three is important.\n\nSecond: Does the response include specific, actionable policies? The reference and samples have detailed strategies, so a YES if they have concrete plans.\n\nThird: Are the policies tailored to regional characteristics? The samples mention specific regions and their unique industries, so this is important.\n\nFourth: Does the response address both short-term and long-term strategies? Some samples mention both, so this could be a criterion.\n\nFifth: Are the policies feasible and realistic? The samples have practical steps, so checking if they are realistic.\n\nSixth: Does the response include data or metrics for evaluation? The reference has KPIs, so this is a key point.\n\nSeventh: Are the policies inclusive of local communities and stakeholders? The samples mention community engagement, so this is important.\n\nEighth: Does the response ensure sustainability and environmental considerations? The samples talk about green initiatives and sustainability, so this is another criterion.\n\nNow, I need to make sure each criterion is specific, binary, and not generic. Let me structure them as per the example given.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 지역 특화 산업, 지역 간 균형 발전, 지방 분권 강화를 모두 포함하는 정책 아이디어를 제시했는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"specificity\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 특정 지역(예: 부산, 제주)이나 산업(예: 수소, 스마트팜)에 맞춘 구체적인 방안을 제시했는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"feasibility\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 현실적인 자원·재정·규제 환경에 맞춘 실행 가능성 있는 정책을 제시했는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"balance\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 지역 간 격차 해소와 경제 활성화의 균형을 동시에 고려했는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"sustainability\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 녹색전환·지속가능성·주민 이익 공유를 위한 정책을 포함했는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"data_driven\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 데이터·실증·성과 지표(KPI)를 기반으로 한 정책을 제시했는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"stakeholder_inclusion\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 지역 주민·기업·대학·정부 등 다각적 이해관계자 참여를 고려했는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"innovation\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 디지털·혁신 기술(예: AI, 클라우드)을 활용한 차별화된 정책을 제시했는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
