sample responses, they all mention structure (like 3 parts, line length), rhythm and meter, imagery and symbolism, thematic elements, and how traditional elements are transformed. So, the criteria should be specific to the prompt and binary (yes/no).\n\nPossible criteria could be:\n\n1. Instruction Following: Does the response address both the comparison of formal features and the inheritance/transformations?\n2. Structural Accuracy: Correctly identifies the 3-part structure of sijo and the free form of modern single verse.\n3. Rhythm and Meter: Correctly describes the traditional meter and the modern free rhythm.\n4. Imagery and Symbolism: Accurately compares traditional symbols with modern ones.\n5. Thematic Analysis: Properly addresses themes like nature, ethics, and social issues.\n6. Inheritance of Aesthetics: Correctly identifies how traditional aesthetics like restraint and white space are maintained.\n7. Transformation of Aesthetics: Correctly explains how traditional elements are adapted in modern poetry.\n8. Clarity and Coherence: The response is clear and logically organized.\n\nEach criterion should be specific, binary, and not generic. Need to ensure that each is a yes/no check based on the response's content. Also, avoid vague advice. Now, structure this into the JSON format as specified.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 시조와 현대 단시의 형식적 특징 비교 및 전통 시가 미학의 계승·변주에 대한 구체적 분석을 포함해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"structural_accuracy\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"시조의 3장 구조(초장-중장-종장)와 현대 단시의 자유 형식이 명확히 구분되어야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"rhythm_meter\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"시조의 4음보 호흡과 현대 단시의 행갈이·공백으로 형성된 리듬 차이가 정확히 설명되어야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"imagery_symbolism\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"전통 상징(달·물)과 현대 사물(네온 빛, 콘크리트)의 재맥락화가 명확히 비교되어야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"thematic_analysis\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"전통의 자연-도덕적 성찰과 현대의 도시-기술적 감각이 구체적으로 분석되어야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"aesthetic_inheritance\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"시조의 절제·여백 미학이 현대 단시의 미니멀리즘·공백 시학으로 계승되었는지 명확히 설명해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"aesthetic_transformation\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"전통의 구어성과 현대의 아이러니·블랙코미디로 변주된 풍자·해학이 구체적으로 제시되어야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"clarity_coherence\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 논리적 구조와 명확한 분할(형식적 특징 vs. 미학 계승)을 통해 독자에게 명확한 이해를 제공해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
