y of the information. The reference response mentions songs that aren't the main answer, but the samples all focus on Britten's piece. So another criterion could be whether the response accurately describes the correct song.\n\nThen, the response should be concise. The reference response is detailed, but the samples are more direct. Maybe a criterion for being to the point.\n\nClarity of the explanation. The reference response explains the songs, but the samples are more about the correct answer. So checking if the explanation is clear and relevant.\n\nRelevance to the query. The reference response includes other songs, but the samples focus on the correct one. So a criterion to ensure the response stays on topic.\n\nCorrectness of the composer and details. The samples mention Britten, so checking if the composer and details are accurate.\n\nUse of specific examples. The reference response gives examples, but the samples are more about the main answer. So a criterion for providing specific examples related to the correct song.\n\nCorrectness of the genre. The reference response mentions orchestral pieces, but the samples are about orchestral music. So checking if the response correctly identifies the genre.\n\nWait, but the user's query is about a song for beginners, so the response should be about a song, not just an orchestral piece. The samples mention Britten's work, which is an orchestral piece. The reference response includes songs like \"Agnus Dei,\" which are choral, not orchestral. So maybe the correct answer is the orchestral piece, but the reference response is a bit off. Hmm, this is a bit confusing. The user's query is about a song for beginners, but the samples all point to the orchestral piece. So the correct answer is the orchestral piece, not the choral ones. Therefore, the criteria should check if the response correctly identifies the orchestral piece by Britten.\n\nSo, the criteria should be:\n\n1. Correct identification of the song (Britten's work).\n2. Accuracy of composer and details.\n3. Relevance to the query (song for beginners).\n4. Correct genre (orchestral).\n5. Specific examples (like the structure of the piece).\n6. Conciseness.\n7. Clarity of explanation.\n8. Correctness of the main answer.\n\nBut need to make sure each criterion is binary and specific. Let me structure them properly.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 \\\"청소년을 위한 관현악 입문\\\"(The Young Person’s Guide to the Orchestra)을 정확히 식별합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"accuracy\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 벤저민 브리튼이 1945년에 작곡했음을 정확히 명시합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"relevance\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 청소년 관현악 입문을 위한 교육용 곡임을 명확히 설명합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"specificity\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 퍼셀의 주제를 바탕으로 한 변주와 푸가로 구성된 구조를 정확히 설명합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"conciseness\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.1,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 과도한 추가 정보 없이 핵심 내용만 명확히 전달합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"clarity\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.1,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 곡의 목적(교육용)과 구조를 명확히 설명합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"correctness\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.1,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 \\\"가사가 있는 곡\\\"이 아닌 순수 기악곡임을 명확히 합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"contextualization\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.1,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 청소년이 함께 부르는 것이 중요함을 교육적 맥락에서 설명합니다.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
