{"prompt_id": "prompt_a08027e01eab", "pair_id": "pair_a47763c767eb", "method": "rrd_pairwise_reference", "generator_family": "qwen_small", "generator_model": "Qwen/Qwen3-4B-FP8", "criteria": [{"id": "F1", "axis": "instruction_following", "importance": "essential", "weight": 0.2941176470588235, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 사용자 요청을 직접적이고 빠짐없이 수행한다. [smoke:c42dfe]", "self_contained": true}, {"id": "F2", "axis": "correctness", "importance": "essential", "weight": 0.2941176470588235, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 사실 오류와 근거 없는 단정을 피하고 정확한 내용을 제공한다. [smoke:0c0edd]", "self_contained": true}, {"id": "F3", "axis": "completeness", "importance": "important", "weight": 0.20588235294117643, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 핵심 요소를 누락하지 않고 필요한 설명을 포함한다. [smoke:1b0826]", "self_contained": true}, {"id": "F4", "axis": "korean_naturalness", "importance": "important", "weight": 0.20588235294117643, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 자연스럽고 읽기 쉬운 한국어 문장을 사용한다. [smoke:b9faef]", "self_contained": true}], "rar_items": [], "generation_metadata": {"fallback_used": "rrd_static_fallback", "errors": ["'\"satisfied\"'"], "auxiliary_sample_ids": ["sample_01", "sample_02", "sample_03", "sample_04", "sample_05", "sample_06", "sample_07", "sample_08"], "reference_guidance_used": true, "raw_output": "<think>\nOkay, I need to create 8 binary criteria (YES/NO) for evaluating the quality of responses to the user's prompt about effective prompting for LLMs. The user provided a reference response and several sample responses. The criteria must be specific to the prompt and not generic.\n\nFirst, I'll look at the reference response. It lists five key points: clarity, context, specific requirements, step-by-step questions, and open-ended questions. The samples also mention things like role specification, output format, constraints, examples, and quality standards.\n\nSo, the criteria should cover aspects like following instructions, providing context, specifying output format, including examples, defining quality standards, ensuring clarity, using step-by-step approaches, and checking for constraints.\n\nLet me list possible criteria:\n\n1. Instruction Following: Does the response address the user's request directly?\n2. Context Provided: Does it include necessary background information?\n3. Output Format Specified: Does it clearly state the desired format?\n4. Examples Included: Are there examples to illustrate the points?\n5. Quality Standards Defined: Are there criteria for quality (accuracy, brevity, etc.)?\n6. Clarity and Specificity: Is the response clear and specific?\n7. Step-by-Step Approach: Does it break down complex tasks into steps?\n8. Constraints and Boundaries: Are there clear constraints or limits?\n\nNow, I need to make sure each criterion is binary (YES/NO) and specific to the prompt. The reference response and samples all mention these elements, so these criteria should be valid. I'll structure them as per the JSON format provided, ensuring each has an ID, axis, importance, weight, polarity, and text in Korean.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 사용자 요청에 직접적으로 대응하며, 프롬프팅의 핵심 원칙과 예시를 명확히 설명합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"context_provided\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 필요한 배경 정보(예: 프롬프트 구조, 템플릿 예시)를 포함하여 맥락을 명확히 제공합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"output_format_specified\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 출력 형식(예: JSON, 불릿, 톤)을 구체적으로 정의하여 사용자 기대에 부합합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"examples_included\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 좋은/나쁜 예시를 포함하여 의도를 명확히 보여줍니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"quality_standards_defined\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 정확성, 간결성, 검증 기준 등을 포함하여 품질 기준을 정의합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"clarity_and_specificity\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 용어 정의, 제약, 금지 사항 등을 구체적으로 명시하여 모호성을 줄입니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"step_by_step_approach\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 복잡한 작업을 단계별로 나누어 처리하는 방법을 제시합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"constraints_and_boundaries\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 금지 사항, 데이터 제약, 시간/비용 제한 등을 명확히 경계합니다.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
