n the countryside. It also mentions solutions like balanced development policies.\n\nLooking at the sample responses, they all elaborate on historical context, economic factors, policy issues, transportation infrastructure, education, labor markets, and the feedback loops between urbanization and rural decline. They also mention the negative effects on both urban and rural areas, such as housing costs, environmental issues, and social problems.\n\nSo, the key elements to cover in the criteria would be:\n\n1. **Instruction Following**: Whether the response directly addresses the causes and effects as requested.\n2. **Historical Context**: Mentioning the historical development leading to urbanization.\n3. **Economic Factors**: Discussing economic policies and industrialization.\n4. **Policy Influence**: Evaluating the role of government policies.\n5. **Transportation Impact**: How transportation infrastructure affects urbanization.\n6. **Education and Labor Markets**: The role of education and job opportunities.\n7. **Feedback Loops**: Identifying the cyclical effects between urbanization and rural decline.\n8. **Consequences Analysis**: Covering the outcomes on both urban and rural areas.\n\nEach criterion should be a binary check. Let me make sure they are specific and not generic. For example, \"Historical Context\" should check if the response includes the historical development from the 1960s to the present. \"Policy Influence\" should check if government policies are discussed. Each of these points is specific to the prompt and can be evaluated as yes or no.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 '수도권 집중 현상과 지방 소멸 문제의 원인과 결과'를 구체적으로 분석하는지 여부\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"historical_context\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 1960~80년대 산업화, 1990년대 서비스화 등 역사적 배경을 포함하는지 여부\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"economic_factors\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 정부 산업화 정책, 경제 성장의 공간적 편중을 분석하는지 여부\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"policy_influence\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 수도권 규제, 공공기관 이전 등 정책의 역할을 평가하는지 여부\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"transportation_impact\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 교통 인프라(고속도로, KTX)의 '빨대 효과'를 설명하는지 여부\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"education_labor\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 교육·의료 인프라의 수도권 집중과 노동 시장 구조를 연결하는지 여부\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"feedback_loops\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 '청년 유출 → 서비스 축소 → 추가 유출' 같은 피드백 루프를 설명하는지 여부\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"consequences_analysis\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 수도권 과밀과 지방 소멸의 사회·경제·국가적 결과를 구체적으로 분석하는지 여부\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
