onse. Let me brainstorm possible criteria:\n\n1. **Instruction Following**: Does the response directly address the task of creative high-end serving methods?\n2. **Use of Premium Ingredients**: Does it suggest using high-quality, premium ingredients?\n3. **Innovative Techniques**: Does it incorporate modern or unique cooking techniques?\n4. **Texture Contrast**: Does it emphasize different textures (crunchy, soft, creamy)?\n5. **Seasonal/Local Ingredients**: Does it mention using seasonal or local produce?\n6. **Service and Presentation**: Does it describe a unique service method or presentation?\n7. **Storytelling/Context**: Does it include a narrative or cultural context?\n8. **Sustainability/Responsibility**: Does it address sustainability or ethical considerations?\n\nNow, I need to ensure these are binary (YES/NO) and specific to the task. Let me check if these are covered in the reference and samples. The reference mentions premium ingredients and service. The samples talk about techniques, textures, local ingredients, service, storytelling, and sustainability. \n\nI think these 8 criteria cover the main aspects. Now, I need to phrase them in Korean as per the JSON structure, making sure they are specific and not generic. Also, each criterion should be a yes/no check based on the response's content.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 한국 길거리 음식을 고급 식당에서 제공할 수 있는 창의적인 방법을 직접적으로 제안합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"premium_ingredients\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 제철 재료, 고급 식재료(트러플, 고추장 등)를 활용한 재료 격상을 제안합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"innovative_techniques\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 저온 조리, 클리어 소스, 퓨레/젤/폼 기법 등 고급 기술을 포함한 재해석을 제안합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"texture_contrast\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 바삭-쫄깃-크리미 등 다층적인 식감 대비를 강조합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"seasonal_local_context\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 제철 수산, 지역 장(간장·청국장)을 활용한 지역성과 계절감을 강조합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"service_presentation\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 테이블사이드 마무리, 미니 카트 서비스 등 독특한 서비스 연출을 제안합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"storytelling_context\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 지역 노점 서사, 골목의 기억을 통한 스토리텔링을 포함합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"sustainability_ethics\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 부산물 재활용, 지속가능한 재료 사용, 알레르기 대안을 포함한 윤리적 접근을 제안합니다.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
