atures\n- Mention of regional focus (VK in CIS, Facebook global)\n- Discussion of specific functions like messaging, groups, ads\n- Regulatory and data privacy aspects\n- Business models and monetization strategies\n- Cultural and community aspects\n- Technical details like algorithms and app integration\n\nNow, I need to translate these into 8 specific criteria. Each should be a binary yes/no check. Let's brainstorm:\n\n1. **Instruction Following**: Does the response address both VK and Facebook? The reference and samples do, so this is essential.\n\n2. **Regional Focus**: Correctly identifies VK's focus on CIS and Facebook's global reach.\n\n3. **Function Comparison**: Lists specific functions like messaging, groups, ads, etc., comparing both platforms.\n\n4. **Regulatory Compliance**: Mentions data privacy, local laws, and government regulations.\n\n5. **Business Model**: Discusses monetization methods like ads, subscriptions, payments.\n\n6. **Cultural/Community Aspects**: Highlights community culture, local events, and user engagement.\n\n7. **Technical Features**: Covers algorithms, app integration, and platform-specific tools.\n\n8. **Accuracy of Information**: Ensures all facts are correct, like VK's establishment year and Facebook's global user base.\n\nWait, but the user said to avoid generic advice. So each criterion should be specific. Let me check if these are all specific and not overlapping. Also, the importance and weight might vary, but the user didn't specify, so I'll set them as per the example.\n\nNow, structure each criterion with the required fields. Make sure they are in Korean as per the example. Avoid copying any text from the samples. Ensure each is a binary check.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 VK와 Facebook의 정의, 기능, 비교를 모두 포함한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"regional_focus\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 VK가 러시아·CIS 중심, Facebook이 글로벌 사용자 기반을 강조한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"function_comparison\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 메시징, 그룹, 광고, 라이브 등 기능 차이를 구체적으로 비교한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"regulatory_compliance\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 러시아 데이터 보관, 정부 검열 요구 사항을 언급한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"business_model\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 VK의 마켓플레이스, Facebook의 광고 생태계를 구체적으로 설명한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"cultural_aspects\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 VK의 지역 커뮤니티 문화, Facebook의 글로벌 네트워크 문화를 구분한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"technical_features\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 알고리즘, 메신저 통합, 미니앱 기능 등 기술적 차이를 언급한다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"accuracy\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 VK의 설립 연도, Facebook의 글로벌 사용자 수 등 정확한 정보를 포함한다.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
