o, the key points from the reference and samples are: instruction following, productivity impact, quality, security, compliance, risk management, innovation, and employee satisfaction. But I need to make sure each criterion is specific and binary.\n\nLet me think of 8 criteria. The first one is instruction following. The response should follow the user's instruction to write a proposal against the ban. So, \"Does the response clearly follow the instruction to write a proposal against the ban?\" That's a yes/no.\n\nNext, does the response address the negative impacts of the ban? The reference response does, so that's another yes/no.\n\nThird, does it propose a controlled usage model? The samples mention controlled use, so that's a criterion.\n\nFourth, does it include security measures? The samples have detailed security aspects, so that's another.\n\nFifth, does it address compliance with regulations? Yes, the samples mention compliance.\n\nSixth, does it provide a risk management plan? The samples have risk mitigation strategies.\n\nSeventh, does it suggest innovation and competitiveness? The reference response talks about staying competitive.\n\nEighth, does it include employee satisfaction or retention? The samples mention that banning could reduce satisfaction.\n\nWait, but I need to make sure each is specific. Let me check again. Maybe the criteria should be:\n\n1. Instruction Following: Does the response clearly follow the instruction to write a proposal against the ban?\n2. Negative Impacts of Ban: Does the response clearly outline the negative impacts of the ban?\n3. Controlled Usage Model: Does the response propose a controlled usage model?\n4. Security Measures: Does the response include detailed security measures?\n5. Compliance with Regulations: Does the response address compliance with regulations?\n6. Risk Management: Does the response include a risk management plan?\n7. Innovation and Competitiveness: Does the response address innovation and competitiveness?\n8. Employee Satisfaction: Does the response consider employee satisfaction or retention?\n\nYes, these are specific and binary. Now, I need to translate these into Korean, assign IDs, and ensure they are in the JSON format as specified.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 '외부 LLM 사용 전면 금지 정책 재고 및 통제된 활용 모델 제안'을 명확히 제시하는지\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"negative_impact_analysis\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 금지 정책이 생산성 저하, 기술 부채, 인재 유치 어려움 등 구체적인 부정적 영향을 설명하는지\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"controlled_usage_model\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 보안·법무 기준을 갖춘 통제된 활용 모델(예: 게이트웨이, 데이터 분류)을 제안하는지\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"security_measures\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 PII/소스코드 자동 마스킹, 프록시 게이트웨이, DLP 연계 등 보안 통제 방안을 포함하는지\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"compliance_address\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 GDPR, SOC2 등 규제 준수를 위한 데이터 처리 계약, 감사 로그 등 정책을 제안하는지\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"risk_management\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 섀도우 IT 리스크, 환각/정확성 문제 등 통제 가능한 리스크 관리 방안을 포함하는지\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"innovation_competitiveness\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 기술 업데이트, 혁신 속도 향상, 경쟁력 유지를 위한 LLM 활용 필요성을 강조하는지\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"employee_satisfaction\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 개발자 만족도, 인재 유치·유지에 대한 영향을 고려하는지\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
