lowing: Does the response address both cities' industries and their economic impacts?\n- Accuracy: Does it correctly describe the industries and their roles?\n- Depth: Does it provide detailed analysis of factors like value chains, economic effects, risks?\n- Structure: Is the response organized logically with clear sections?\n- Specificity: Does it mention specific data or examples?\n- Relevance: Does it stay focused on the comparison and economic impact?\n- Clarity: Is the information presented clearly and concisely?\n- Originality: Does it offer unique insights beyond surface-level information?\n\nNow, I need to translate these into 8 binary criteria. Each should be a specific check that can be answered YES or NO. They must be prompt-specific, so they should relate directly to the user's request about comparing Incheon's port and Busan's automotive industries and their economic impacts.\n\nPossible criteria:\n1. Instruction Following: Does the response address both cities' industries and their economic impacts?\n2. Accuracy: Correctly describes the industries and their roles.\n3. Depth of Analysis: Provides detailed analysis of factors like value chains, economic effects, risks.\n4. Logical Structure: Organized with clear sections.\n5. Specificity: Mentions specific data or examples.\n6. Relevance: Focuses on the comparison and economic impact.\n7. Clarity: Clearly presented information.\n8. Originality: Offers unique insights beyond surface-level information.\n\nI need to ensure each criterion is specific to the prompt and can be evaluated as YES or NO. Also, avoid generic advice. Check if these criteria cover the key aspects of the reference and sample responses. Make sure they are not overlapping and each is distinct.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 인천의 항구 산업과 울산의 자동차 산업을 비교 분석하고, 지역 경제에 미치는 영향을 깊이 있게 조사하는 데 집중되어야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"accuracy\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 두 도시의 산업 구조, 역사적 발전 경로, 경제적 영향에 대한 정확한 정보를 제공해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"depth_of_analysis\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 산업 가치사슬, 공급망, 지역 경제 파급효과, 리스크 등에 대한 심층 분석이 포함되어야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"logical_structure\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 체계적인 구조로 조직되어, 비교 분석의 핵심 요소를 명확히 나누고 연결해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"specificity\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 구체적인 데이터(예: 물동량, 생산량, 고용 수치)나 사례를 포함해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"relevance\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 사용자 요청에 직접적으로 관련된 내용만 포함해야 하며, 편향된 정보나 불필요한 추가 내용은 배제해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"clarity\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 명확하고 일관된 언어로 작성되어, 독자에게 이해하기 쉬어야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"originality\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 표준적인 분석을 넘어, 두 도시의 산업 전환, 지속가능성, 지역 경제의 구조적 차이에 대한 독창적인 시사점을 제시해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
