roblem statement, including specific campaign ideas, ensuring the campaign is creative, addressing social issues, being data-driven, having measurable outcomes, and being culturally appropriate.\n\nLet me list possible criteria:\n\n1. **Instruction Following**: Does the response address both explaining the problem and proposing a creative campaign?\n2. **Problem Explanation**: Does it clearly outline the severity of the issue (high alcohol consumption and social problems)?\n3. **Campaign Specificity**: Are the campaign ideas detailed and actionable?\n4. **Creativity**: Are the ideas innovative and not generic?\n5. **Social Impact**: Does it address the social issues like violence, accidents, etc.?\n6. **Data-Driven**: Does it reference data or statistics?\n7. **Measurable Outcomes**: Does it include specific metrics or KPIs?\n8. **Cultural Appropriateness**: Are the ideas suitable for the Korean context?\n\nNow, I need to make sure each criterion is binary and specific. For example, \"Instruction Following\" would check if both parts of the query are addressed. \"Problem Explanation\" checks if the severity is clearly stated. \"Campaign Specificity\" ensures the ideas are detailed. \"Creativity\" checks if the ideas are unique. \"Social Impact\" ensures the campaign addresses the mentioned social issues. \"Data-Driven\" checks for data references. \"Measurable Outcomes\" looks for KPIs. \"Cultural Appropriateness\" ensures the ideas fit the Korean context.\n\nI need to ensure that each criterion is not generic. For example, instead of saying \"good structure,\" it should be specific to the prompt. Also, avoid using terms like \"good writing advice\" as per the user's instruction.\n\nNow, I'll structure each criterion with the required fields, ensuring they are binary and specific.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 한국 사회의 음주율과 사회적 문제를 설명하고, 창의적인 캠페인 아이디어를 구체적으로 제안해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"problem_explanation\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 음주율의 심각성과 사회적 문제(폭력, 교통사고, 건강 문제 등)를 명확히 설명해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"campaign_specificity\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 구체적인 캠페인 아이디어(예: 전시회, 캠페인 이름, 실행 단계)를 구체적으로 제안해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"creativity\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 일반적인 음주 예방 메시지 대신 창의적인 접근(예: D.R.I.N.K. 캠페인)을 제안해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"social_impact\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 사회적 문제(폭력, 교통사고, 가정폭력 등)를 해결하는 데 중점을 두어야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"data_driven\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 WHO, OECD 등 신뢰할 수 있는 데이터를 인용하여 문제의 심각성을 지지해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"measurable_outcomes\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 캠페인의 성과(예: 음주율 감소, 무알코올 매출 비중)를 구체적으로 측정할 수 있는 지표를 제안해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"cultural_appropriateness\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 한국 사회의 문화적 맥락(예: 회식 문화, 청소년 음주 트렌드)에 맞는 아이디어를 제안해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
