\n\nThe criteria must be specific to the prompt and binary (YES/NO). They should focus on essential aspects like following the instruction, accuracy, use of historical data, and clarity. Let me think of possible criteria:\n\n1. Instruction Following: Does the response directly address the question about total agricultural production during the war?\n2. Historical Data Use: Does it reference historical records or estimates?\n3. War Impact Consideration: Does it account for the war's effects on production?\n4. Uncertainty Acknowledgment: Does it mention the uncertainty in estimates?\n5. Numerical Estimation: Does it provide a numerical range or value?\n6. Contextual Accuracy: Does it correctly contextualize the production within the war period?\n7. Source of Data: Does it cite sources or methods for the estimation?\n8. Clarity and Conciseness: Is the response clear and to the point without unnecessary details?\n\nWait, the user said to avoid vague or generic advice. So each criterion should be specific. Let me check the reference response again. It gives a range, mentions the war's impact, uses historical data, and acknowledges uncertainty. The samples also vary in their approach, some with detailed calculations, others more general.\n\nSo, the criteria should be things like:\n\n- Does the response estimate the total agricultural production during the war?\n- Does it reference historical data or sources?\n- Does it account for the war's impact on production?\n- Does it acknowledge the uncertainty in the estimate?\n- Does it provide a numerical range or value?\n- Does it correctly contextualize the production within the war period?\n- Does it explain the methodology or assumptions?\n- Does it avoid overgeneralization or speculation?\n\nBut need to make sure each is binary. Let me adjust:\n\n1. Instruction Following: Directly addresses the question about total agricultural production during the war.\n2. Historical Data Use: References historical records or estimates.\n3. War Impact Consideration: Accounts for the war's effects on production.\n4. Uncertainty Acknowledgment: Mentions the uncertainty in the estimate.\n5. Numerical Estimation: Provides a numerical range or value.\n6. Contextual Accuracy: Correctly contextualizes the production within the war period.\n7. Methodology Explanation: Explains the methodology or assumptions.\n8. Avoiding Overgeneralization: Avoids overgeneralization or speculation.\n\nBut need to check if these are specific enough. Also, the reference response mentions the war's impact, uncertainty, and provides a numerical range. The samples have varying levels of detail. So the criteria should be based on these aspects. Let me finalize the 8 criteria.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 임진왜란 기간 동안 한반도의 총 농업 생산량을 직접 추정하는 것이어야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"historical_context\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 조선 시대의 농업 생산량 추정 기준(예: 인구, 1인당 소비량)을 언급해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"war_impact\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 전쟁으로 인한 생산량 감소(예: 경작지 파괴, 전염병)를 반영해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"uncertainty\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 추정의 불확실성(예: 단위 환산, 사료 부족)을 명시해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"numerical_range\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 생산량을 수치 범위(예: 1.06~1.49억 석)로 제공해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"methodology\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 추정 방법(예: 인구 기반 계산, 전쟁 충격 가정)을 설명해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"contextual_accuracy\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 전쟁 기간과 평년 생산량의 비교를 명시해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"avoid_overgeneralization\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 지역 간 편차(예: 남부 vs 북부)를 고려해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
{"prompt_id": "prompt_c5367259f135", "pair_id": "pair_dbcf8ab05f9f", "method": "rrd_pairwise_reference", "generator_family": "qwen_small", "generator_model": "Qwen/Qwen3-4B-FP8", "criteria": [{"id": "F1", "axis": "instruction_following", "importance": "essential", "weight": 0.2941176470588235, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 사용자 요청을 직접적이고 빠짐없이 수행한다. [smoke:a5bf36]", "self_contained": true}, {"id": "F2", "axis": "correctness", "importance": "essential", "weight": 0.2941176470588235, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 사실 오류와 근거 없는 단정을 피하고 정확한 내용을 제공한다. [smoke:dd0596]", "self_contained": true}, {"id": "F3", "axis": "completeness", "importance": "important", "weight": 0.20588235294117643, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 핵심 요소를 누락하지 않고 필요한 설명을 포함한다. [smoke:6cdc61]", "self_contained": true}, {"id": "F4", "axis": "korean_naturalness", "importance": "important", "weight": 0.20588235294117643, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 자연스럽고 읽기 쉬운 한국어 문장을 사용한다. [smoke:c8b224]", "self_contained": true}], "rar_items": [], "generation_metadata": {"fallback_used": "rrd_static_fallback", "errors": ["Connection error."], "auxiliary_sample_ids": ["sample_01", "sample_02", "sample_03", "sample_04", "sample_05", "sample_06", "sample_07", "sample_08"], "reference_guidance_used": true, "raw_output": "<think>\nOkay, I need to create a JSON with 8 criteria for evaluating the responses to the user's query about the impact of volcanic activity and climate on the geomorphology and ecology of Jeju Island. The user provided a reference response and several sample responses. The criteria must be specific to the prompt, binary (YES/NO), and not vague or generic.\n\nFirst, I'll look at the reference response and the samples to identify key elements that are essential. The reference talks about volcanic activity forming the landscape, like the Hallasan volcano, and how the climate (marine climate) affects the ecosystem. The samples elaborate on specific features like the formation of volcanic landforms, the role of hydrothermal activity, the impact of wind and sea currents, and the resulting ecosystems such as the ginseng forest and cave ecosystems.\n\nSo, possible criteria could be:\n\n1. **Volcanic Activity and Landform Formation**: Does the response mention the formation of specific volcanic features like Hallasan, volcanic cones, or lava tubes?\n2. **Climate's Role in Ecosystem Development**: Does it discuss how the marine climate influences the ecosystem, like the presence of diverse flora and fauna?\n3. **Hydrological Features**: Does it address the role of groundwater and the lack of surface rivers due to volcanic rock?\n4. **Microclimates and Ecosystem Diversity**: Does it explain how microclimates created by volcanic features lead to diverse ecosystems?\n5. **Impact of Wind and Sea Currents**: Does it mention the influence of strong winds and sea currents on the landscape and ecology?\n6. **Special Ecosystems**: Does it discuss unique ecosystems like the ginseng forest or cave ecosystems?\n7. **Human-Environment Interaction**: Does it touch on how human activities interact with the natural environment, like traditional farming practices?\n8. **Geological and Climatic Interactions**: Does it explain the interaction between geological features and climate in shaping the landscape and ecology?\n\nI need to ensure each criterion is specific, binary, and not generic. Let me check if these are covered in the samples. The samples do mention specific landforms, climate effects, hydrology, microclimates, wind and sea currents, unique ecosystems, human interaction, and geological-climatic interactions. So these 8 criteria should work. Now, I'll structure them into JSON with the required fields.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 화산활동과 기후의 상호작용이 지형과 생태계 형성에 미친 영향을 구체적인 지형(예: 한라산, 용암동굴)과 생태계(예: 곶자왈, 해양생태계)를 중심으로 분석했는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 기후적 특성(예: 해양성 난대 기후, 강풍)이 지형의 미세기후와 식생 분포에 미친 영향을 명확히 설명했는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 화산활동이 만든 지하수 체계(예: 용천, 지하수 흐름)와 토양 특성(예: 화산회토, 투수성)이 생태계 형성에 미친 영향을 다루었는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 지형-기후 상호작용이 만들어낸 고도대별 생태대(예: 아고산대 구상나무림, 중산간 곶자왈)와 미세서식지 다양성을 설명했는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 해양성 기후와 강풍이 해안 생태계(예: 암반조간대, 연산호 군락)와 인간-자연 상호작용(예: 돌담 농경)에 미친 영향을 분석했는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 화산활동과 기후가 만들어낸 고유 생태계(예: 동굴 생물군, 곶자왈)와 생물다양성의 특이성을 명확히 제시했는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 지형-기후 상호작용이 지표수 부족과 지하수 의존성, 토양 침식 위험 등 생태계 취약성을 설명했는가?\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 화산활동과 기후가 지형과 생태계에 미친 영향을 종합적으로 연결해, 섬의 독특한 자연 경관과 생물다양성의 근본 원인을 명확히 제시했는가?\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
