or adaptation.\n\nThe criteria need to be specific, binary (YES/NO), and not vague. Let me brainstorm possible criteria. \n\n1. **Instruction Following**: Does the response address the main points of the prompt? The reference response does, so this is essential.\n\n2. **Cultural Sensitivity**: Does it acknowledge the cultural differences between standard and dialectal Korean? The reference and samples do mention this.\n\n3. **Personal Perspective**: Does it express empathy from the viewpoint of someone moving to Seoul? The samples do this well.\n\n4. **Specific Examples**: Does it provide concrete examples of communication issues? The reference and samples have examples like pronunciation and expressions.\n\n5. **Adaptation Strategies**: Does it offer practical advice for adapting? The samples include tips like adjusting tone and using standard phrases.\n\n6. **Tone and Nuance**: Does it discuss the nuances of tone and speech patterns? The samples mention tone differences and how they affect communication.\n\n7. **Emotional Impact**: Does it convey the emotional challenges of adaptation? The samples talk about feelings of discomfort and self-doubt.\n\n8. **Clarity and Structure**: Is the response well-organized and clear? The reference response is structured with numbered points, so this is important.\n\nNow, I need to make sure each criterion is specific and binary. Let me check if these are all covered and if they are not too generic. Also, ensure that each criterion is not just a general advice but something that can be judged as YES or NO based on the response.\n\nI think these 8 criteria cover the main aspects. Now, I'll structure them into JSON with the required fields.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 표준어와 방언 차이가 유발하는 의사소통 문제와 적응 과정에 대한 구체적인 사례와 감정적 공감을 포함합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"cultural_sensitivity\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 지역 문화와 서울 중심 문화의 차이가 상호작용에 미치는 영향을 명확히 설명합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"perspective_taking\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 지방에서 서울로 이주한 사람의 주관적 경험과 감정을 체계적으로 반영합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"specific_examples\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 발음 차이, 문화적 표현, 구조 차이 등 구체적인 사례를 제시합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"adaptation_strategies\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 언어 적응을 위한 실질적인 방법(예: 공간 나누기, 표현 선택)을 제시합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"tone_nuance\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.1,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 억양, 속도, 말투 차이가 의사소통에 미치는 영향을 분석합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"emotional_impact\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.1,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 어색함, 위축감, 정체성 혼란 등 감정적 경험을 구체적으로 묘사합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"clarity_structure\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.1,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 논리적 구조와 명확한 분류(예: 1. 발음 차이, 2. 문화적 표현 등)를 유지합니다.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
