timodal data. Another sample includes issues like query understanding, chunking, multi-hop reasoning, faithfulness, temporal drift, evaluation gaps, efficiency, domain adaptation, and security.\n\nSo, the main challenges seem to be: 1) Faithfulness and attribution, 2) Retrieval quality and multi-hop reasoning, 3) Chunking and context management, 4) Temporal and freshness issues, 5) Evaluation and benchmarking, 6) Efficiency and cost, 7) Domain adaptation and robustness, 8) Security and privacy. \n\nEach of these should be a criterion. They need to be binary (yes/no) and specific to the prompt. Let me check if these are all relevant and not too generic. The user's prompt is about RAG challenges, so these criteria should directly relate to that. \n\nI need to make sure each criterion is clear and specific. For example, \"Faithfulness and Attribution\" would check if the response addresses the accuracy of the generated text in relation to the retrieved sources. \"Retrieval Quality and Multi-hop Reasoning\" would check if the response covers the effectiveness of retrieval and handling of multi-step queries. \n\nI should avoid generic terms like \"good quality\" and focus on specific aspects mentioned in the samples. Also, each criterion should be a yes/no check. Let me structure them based on the key points from the samples.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 RAG 연구의 최근 주요 과제(예: 근거 정합성, 다단계 추론, 데이터 품질)를 정확히 언급했는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"depth_of_analysis\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 각 과제에 구체적인 연구 아이디어(예: 근거 강제 디코딩, 멀티홉 플래닝)를 제시했는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"relevance_to_domain\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 RAG의 특성(예: 검색-생성 파이프라인, 구조화 데이터 처리)과의 연관성을 고려했는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"practical_implication\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 연구 아이디어의 실용성(예: 비용 최적화, 안전성 강화)을 평가했는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"completeness_of_coverage\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 RAG의 다양한 측면(예: 시간 인식, 멀티모달 처리, 보안)을 포괄적으로 다뤘는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"clarity_of_explanation\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.1,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 과제와 연구 아이디어의 연결성을 명확히 설명했는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"originality_of_thinking\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.1,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 최근 연구 동향(예: Self-RAG, GraphRAG)을 반영한 독창적인 시각을 제시했는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"feasibility_of_implementation\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.1,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 연구 아이디어의 구현 가능성(예: 벤치마크, 도구 활용)을 제시했는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
