n Following: Does the response address both poets and their natural expressions and love themes?\n2. Natural Imagery: Does it accurately compare the natural elements in both poems?\n3. Language Style: Does it distinguish between the poetic styles of the two poets?\n4. Emotional Expression: Does it clearly contrast the emotional tones of love in both poems?\n5. Time and Space Structure: Does it analyze the temporal and spatial aspects of each poem?\n6. Thematic Depth: Does it delve into the deeper themes of love and nature?\n7. Structural Clarity: Does the response have a clear structure with distinct sections?\n8. Critical Insight: Does it provide insightful analysis beyond surface-level comparison?\n\nWait, the user wants 8 criteria, each binary. Let me check if these are specific enough. Maybe \"Natural Imagery\" is too broad. Let me think again.\n\nLooking at the samples, they mention specific elements like the use of natural symbols, the role of nature in expressing love, the language's rhythm, and the time structure. So, maybe:\n\n1. Instruction Following: Does the response address both poets and their natural expressions and love themes?\n2. Natural Imagery Comparison: Does it compare the natural elements in both poems?\n3. Language Style Contrast: Does it distinguish between the poetic styles of the two poets?\n4. Emotional Tone Contrast: Does it contrast the emotional expressions of love in both poems?\n5. Time and Space Analysis: Does it analyze the temporal and spatial aspects of each poem?\n6. Thematic Depth: Does it explore deeper themes like love and nature's role?\n7. Structural Organization: Does the response have a clear structure with distinct sections?\n8. Critical Insight: Does it provide insightful analysis beyond surface-level comparison?\n\nBut need to make sure each is binary. Also, the criteria should be in Korean as per the example. Let me adjust the names to be in Korean and ensure they are specific. Also, check if the samples have these aspects. The reference and samples do discuss natural imagery, language style, emotional tone, time/space, and structure. So these 8 criteria should cover those aspects.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 김소월과 김영랑의 시를 비교 분석하며, 두 시인의 자연 표현 방식과 사랑의 정서 차이를 명확히 다룬다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"natural_imagery_comparison\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 두 시의 자연 이미지(진달래 vs 모란)를 구체적·토속적 vs 상징적·관능적 형태로 구분하여 비교한다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"language_style_distinction\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 두 시의 언어 스타일(민요적 구어체 vs 정제된 서정어법)을 구체적으로 구분하여 분석한다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"emotional_tone_contrast\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 두 시의 사랑 정서(소월의 체념 vs 영랑의 미의 절정)를 명확히 구분하여 설명한다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"temporal_spatial_analysis\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 두 시의 시간·공간 구조(이별의 순간 vs 계절의 리듬)를 비교 분석한다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"thematic_depth\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 자연과 사랑의 관계(정화의 매개 vs 미의 법칙)를 철저히 탐구한다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"structural_organization\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 논리적 구조(이상·분석·결론)를 명확히 유지하여 독자에게 명확한 흐름을 제공한다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"critical_insight\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 두 시인의 미학적 차이(민요적 토속 정서 vs 근대적 미의식)를 깊이 있게 해석한다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
