terials can't be exactly that, so materials close to εr=1 with low loss and proper design are better. It also mentions the importance of shape, placement, and other factors.\n\nLooking at the sample responses, they all agree that εr≈1 is ideal but emphasize the need for low tanδ, proper material selection, shape optimization, and other factors. They also mention specific materials like foams and the importance of testing and calibration.\n\nNow, I need to identify the key aspects that the reference response highlights. The reference talks about instruction following, material properties (εr, tanδ, μr), shape optimization, placement, testing methods, and the importance of combining these factors.\n\nSo, the rubric criteria should cover:\n\n1. Instruction Following: Does the response directly address the question about εr=1 and its suitability?\n2. Material Properties: Does it mention εr≈1, low tanδ, and μr≈1?\n3. Shape Optimization: Does it discuss shape design to minimize scattering?\n4. Placement Considerations: Does it talk about placement to avoid interference?\n5. Testing Methods: Does it mention testing techniques like time gating or background subtraction?\n6. Material Examples: Does it provide specific examples of materials close to εr=1?\n7. Trade-offs: Does it address trade-offs between material properties and structural requirements?\n8. Comprehensive Approach: Does it emphasize the combination of material, shape, placement, and testing?\n\nEach of these points needs to be a binary YES/NO. Let me check if these are specific enough and not too vague. The reference and samples all mention these points, so these criteria should be valid.\n\nNow, I need to translate these into Korean, ensuring they are prompt-specific. For example, \"Instruction Following\" would be about whether the response directly answers the question. \"Material Properties\" would check if εr≈1, low tanδ, and μr≈1 are mentioned.\n\nI should make sure each criterion is clear and not overlapping. Also, avoid generic advice. The reference and samples all focus on specific aspects, so the criteria should reflect that.\n\nLet me structure each criterion with the correct ID, axis, importance, weight, and text in Korean. The self_contained flag should be true for each since they are binary and specific.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 유전율 1에 가까운 소재가 RCS 시험 치구에 유리하다는 점을 직접적으로 설명합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"material_properties\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 유전율(εr)≈1, 손실탄젠트(tanδ) 낮음, 비자성(μr≈1) 재료의 중요성을 명시합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"shape_optimization\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 치구 형상(테이퍼/오지브)로 산란 최소화를 위한 설계를 제안합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"placement_consideration\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 치구 배치(안테나 시선 외부, 음영 영역)를 통해 산란 영향 최소화를 제안합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"testing_methods\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 시간게이팅, 배경 제거, 치구 단독 측정 등 측정 기법을 언급합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"material_examples\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 Rohacell, EPS 등 εr≈1.03–1.1의 저밀도 폼을 구체적으로 제안합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"trade_offs\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 기계적 강성과 εr, tanδ의 균형 유지 필요성을 강조합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"comprehensive_approach\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.15,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 재료, 형상, 배치, 측정 기법을 종합적으로 최적화해야 함을 강조합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
