{"prompt_id": "prompt_05e652a1f9e2", "pair_id": "pair_e5f486d52b30", "method": "rrd_pairwise_reference", "generator_family": "qwen_small", "generator_model": "Qwen/Qwen3-4B-FP8", "criteria": [{"id": "F1", "axis": "instruction_following", "importance": "essential", "weight": 0.2941176470588235, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 사용자 요청을 직접적이고 빠짐없이 수행한다. [smoke:4be2e8]", "self_contained": true}, {"id": "F2", "axis": "correctness", "importance": "essential", "weight": 0.2941176470588235, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 사실 오류와 근거 없는 단정을 피하고 정확한 내용을 제공한다. [smoke:7f8d10]", "self_contained": true}, {"id": "F3", "axis": "completeness", "importance": "important", "weight": 0.20588235294117643, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 핵심 요소를 누락하지 않고 필요한 설명을 포함한다. [smoke:acf2ba]", "self_contained": true}, {"id": "F4", "axis": "korean_naturalness", "importance": "important", "weight": 0.20588235294117643, "polarity": "positive", "text_ko": "응답은 자연스럽고 읽기 쉬운 한국어 문장을 사용한다. [smoke:bd7334]", "self_contained": true}], "rar_items": [], "generation_metadata": {"fallback_used": "rrd_static_fallback", "errors": ["'\"satisfied\"'"], "auxiliary_sample_ids": ["sample_01", "sample_02", "sample_03", "sample_04", "sample_05", "sample_06", "sample_07", "sample_08"], "reference_guidance_used": true, "raw_output": "<think>\nOkay, let's tackle this. The user wants me to create 8 criteria for evaluating the responses to the query about the rise of Korean BBQ and its impact on global perceptions of Korean cuisine. The reference response is a survey about perceptions and reasons for the popularity. The sample responses are detailed analyses with various points.\n\nFirst, I need to make sure each criterion is specific to the prompt and can be judged as YES or NO. They should be binary and not vague. Let me look at the reference and samples to find key aspects.\n\nThe reference mentions a survey with 3,000 consumers across 18 countries. The samples discuss factors like Hallyu, social media, interactive dining, taste, supply chain, etc. So, the criteria should cover these elements.\n\nLooking at the samples, common themes are: following the instruction (analyzing reasons and effects), cultural influence (Hallyu), social media presence, interactive dining experience, taste profile, supply chain and infrastructure, global expansion, and impact on Korean cuisine perception.\n\nWait, the user said the criteria should be binary and specific. Let me think of 8 specific aspects. Maybe:\n\n1. Instruction Followed: Did the response analyze the reasons for the rise and the effects on Korean cuisine perception?\n2. Cultural Influence: Mentioned Hallyu (K-pop, dramas) as a factor.\n3. Social Media Presence: Highlighted how social media platforms like YouTube, TikTok contributed.\n4. Interactive Dining Experience: Emphasized the participatory aspect of BBQ.\n5. Taste Profile: Described the unique taste that's universally appealing.\n6. Supply Chain and Infrastructure: Talked about the global supply chain and franchise models.\n7. Global Expansion: Mentioned the spread to different regions and markets.\n8. Impact on Korean Cuisine Perception: Addressed how it changed global views on Korean food.\n\nEach of these can be a criterion. Now, I need to make sure they are binary. For example, does the response address the reasons and effects? Yes/No. Similarly for each point. Let me check if these are specific enough and not generic. The reference and samples all touch on these points, so these criteria should work. Now, structure them into JSON with the required fields.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 한국 바비큐의 세계적 인기 원인과 전 세계 한국 요리 인식 변화를 분석하는 구체적 요인을 제시했는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"cultural_influence\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 한류(음악·드라마)가 K-BBQ 인기를 촉진했는지에 대한 설명이 포함되어 있나?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"social_media_presence\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 소셜미디어(유튜브, TikTok)가 K-BBQ의 글로벌 확산에 기여했는지에 대한 언급이 있나?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"interactive_dining\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 '직접 구워 먹는' 참여형 식경험의 역할을 분석했는가?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"taste_profile\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 K-BBQ의 달고 짭짤한 맛과 매운맛 조합이 글로벌 수용성에 기여했는지에 대한 설명이 있나?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"supply_chain\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 글로벌 프랜차이즈와 유통 인프라가 K-BBQ 확산에 기여했는지에 대한 언급이 있나?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"global_expansion\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 K-BBQ가 북미·동남아·중동 등 다양한 지역으로 확산했는지에 대한 분석이 포함되어 있나?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"perception_shift\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 K-BBQ가 한국 요리 인식을 '맵고 발효된 음식'에서 '메인스트림 요리'로 전환했는지에 대한 설명이 있나?\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
