nd career education.\n\nNow, I need to think of criteria that assess whether the response addresses these aspects. Let me brainstorm possible rubrics:\n\n1. **Instruction Following**: Does the response directly address the causes and effects as requested?\n2. **Cause Analysis**: Does it thoroughly analyze the structural and cultural causes?\n3. **Effect Analysis**: Does it clearly outline the social and economic consequences?\n4. **Policy Proposals**: Are there specific, actionable policy reforms?\n5. **Policy Specificity**: Are the proposed policies detailed and tailored to the problem?\n6. **Feasibility**: Are the policies realistic and implementable?\n7. **Comprehensiveness**: Does it cover all aspects of the problem (causes, effects, solutions)?\n8. **Clarity and Structure**: Is the response well-organized and easy to follow?\n\nWait, the user mentioned that the rubrics should be binary (YES/NO) and not generic. Also, they should be prompt-specific. Let me refine these ideas into 8 specific criteria.\n\n1. **Instruction Followed**: Does the response address the causes and effects of high education enthusiasm and excessive private tutoring, and propose policy reforms?\n2. **Cause Analysis**: Does it thoroughly analyze structural and cultural causes (e.g., historical, cultural, institutional factors)?\n3. **Effect Analysis**: Does it clearly outline the social and economic consequences (e.g., student well-being, inequality, education system issues)?\n4. **Policy Proposals**: Does it include specific, actionable policy reforms (e.g., exam system changes, public education strengthening)?\n5. **Policy Specificity**: Are the proposed policies detailed and tailored to the problem (e.g., specific measures like AI tutoring, public after-school programs)?\n6. **Feasibility**: Are the policies realistic and implementable within the current system?\n7. **Comprehensiveness**: Does it cover all aspects of the problem (causes, effects, solutions)?\n8. **Clarity and Structure**: Is the response well-organized and logically structured?\n\nI need to ensure each rubric is specific to the prompt and not generic. Also, they should be binary. Let me check if these are appropriate. The reference response includes all these elements, so the rubrics should evaluate whether the response meets these points. Now, I'll structure them into JSON format as specified.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 한국 사회의 교육열과 사교육 문제의 원인, 결과, 해결 방안을 분석하고 교육 정책 개혁안을 제시하는 요청을 완전히 따르고 있다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"cause_analysis\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 역사적·문화적·제도적 요인을 포함한 구조적 원인을 체계적으로 분석하고 있다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"effect_analysis\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 학생 건강, 사회적 불평등, 교육 시스템 약화 등 결과를 명확히 설명하고 있다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"policy_proposals\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 대입 제도 개혁, 공교육 강화, 사교육 시장 규제 등 구체적인 정책안을 제시하고 있다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"policy_specificity\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 AI 튜터링, 방과후 프로그램, 직업교육 확대 등 구체적인 실행 방안을 포함하고 있다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"feasibility\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 현실적인 재정·행정·사회적 조건을 고려한 실행 가능성을 제시하고 있다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"comprehensiveness\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 원인, 결과, 해결 방안을 단계별로 체계적으로 연결하여 전체적인 문제 해결을 제시하고 있다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"clarity_structure\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 단기·중기·장기 로드맵과 성과지표를 구분하여 논리적 구조가 명확하고 직관적이다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
