response covers all these aspects. So, the criteria should be specific to the task. Let me think of 8 criteria that are binary (yes/no) and relevant.\n\n1. **Instruction Following**: Does the response address both listing materials and marketing ideas? The reference does both, so this is essential.\n\n2. **Comprehensive Material List**: Does it cover a wide range of materials? The reference lists many, so this is important.\n\n3. **Clear Categorization**: Are materials grouped into categories like construction, interior, etc.? The reference does this, so yes.\n\n4. **Global Appeal**: Are the materials and marketing ideas suitable for global markets? The reference includes eco-friendly and unique features, so yes.\n\n5. **Practical Marketing Ideas**: Are there actionable marketing strategies? The reference has specific ideas like search functions and direct inquiries, so yes.\n\n6. **Clarity and Structure**: Is the information well-organized and easy to follow? The reference uses bullet points and lists, so yes.\n\n7. **Cultural Relevance**: Does it incorporate Korean cultural elements? The reference mentions specific Korean companies and traditional methods, so yes.\n\n8. **Usefulness for Global Consumers**: Are the materials and ideas applicable to international audiences? The reference includes eco-friendly and unique features, so yes.\n\nNow, I need to make sure each criterion is specific, binary, and not generic. Also, avoid copying phrases from the reference. Let me check if these criteria are distinct and cover the key aspects. Yes, they do. Now, format them into JSON with the required structure.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 한국 재료 목록 작성과 마케팅 아이디어 제시를 모두 포함해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"comprehensive_coverage\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"재료 범위가 다양한지(건물, 식품, 식료품 등) 확인해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"category_organization\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"재료가 구분된 카테고리(내부·외부·환경 등)로 정리되어 있는지 확인해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"global_relevance\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"글로벌 시장에서 활용 가능한 재료(환경 친화적, 독특한 특징 등)를 포함하는지 확인해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"actionable_marketing\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"마케팅 아이디어가 구체적이고 실행 가능한지(예: 패키징, 콘텐츠 전략 등) 확인해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"clarity_and_structure\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.1,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"정보가 명확하고 구조화되어 있는지(예: 목록, 테이블, 구분된 섹션 등) 확인해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"cultural_context\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.1,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"한국의 전통·지리·제조법 등 문화적 배경이 반영되어 있는지 확인해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"international_applicability\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.1,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"글로벌 소비자에게 유용한 재료와 마케팅 전략이 포함되어 있는지 확인해야 합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
