personal names (이름). The samples also break down these into percentages and explain the context of the policies like 창씨개명 (creation of Japanese surnames) and 개명 (name change).\n\nSo, the first criteria could be about whether the response mentions the approximate percentage of people using Japanese surnames (성). The reference says around 80%, and the samples all include this. So that's a key point.\n\nNext, the second criterion could be about the percentage of people who changed their personal names (개명), which the samples mention as 10-15%. That's another essential point.\n\nThen, the third criterion might be whether the response explains the context of the policies, like the 창씨개명 and the administrative pressure. The samples do mention these, so that's important.\n\nFourth, the response should address the difference between using a Japanese surname versus a full Japanese name. The samples clarify that using a surname is different from changing the personal name, so that's a key distinction.\n\nFifth, the response should mention the time frame, like 1939-1940, when the policies were implemented. The samples all reference this period, so that's a necessary point.\n\nSixth, the response should include the impact on official documents and daily life, as the samples mention that even if names weren't changed, people used Japanese surnames in official contexts.\n\nSeventh, the response should differentiate between legal registration and actual usage. The samples note that some people might have legal names but not use them in daily life, so that's important.\n\nEighth, the response should provide a range of estimates, like 75-85% for surnames and 10-15% for full names, as the samples do. This shows the uncertainty in the estimates.\n\nI need to make sure each criterion is binary and specific. Let me check if these points are covered and if they are not too vague. The criteria should be about whether the response includes specific elements, not general advice. The reference and samples all include these elements, so the criteria should be based on their presence.\n\nNow, translating these into the required JSON format with the correct structure. Each criterion has an ID, axis, importance, weight, polarity, text in Korean, and self_contained. The weight is 0.5 for essential, and the rest can be 0.25. The text should be concise and specific.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 일제강점기 일본식 성(氏) 사용 비율(약 80%)을 명시합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 일본식 이름(개명) 사용 비율(약 10~15%)을 명시합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 창씨개명 정책의 행정적 압박을 설명합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 성 사용과 이름 변경의 구분을 명시합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 1939~1940년 창씨개명 시기의 중요성을 설명합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 공식 문서에서 일본식 성 사용의 확산을 설명합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 법적 등록과 실제 사용의 차이를 설명합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 추정 범위(75~85% / 10~15%)를 수치적으로 제공합니다.\",\n      \"self_contained\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
