he most preferred for cost and safety, with NMC/NCA for high performance, and LTO for specific applications.\n\nNow, I need to create 8 binary criteria (YES/NO) that are specific to the prompt and based on the reference. The criteria should be essential and not vague. Let me think about the key aspects that the reference and samples highlight.\n\nFirst, the reference and samples mention LFP as the most preferred due to cost, safety, and longevity. So one criterion could be whether the response identifies LFP as the primary choice. Another is if it explains the cost advantage of LFP. Then, safety is a key point, so checking if the response emphasizes safety. Performance balance between cost and performance is another aspect.\n\nAlso, the samples mention NMC/NCA for high performance, so a criterion could be if the response includes NMC/NCA as an alternative. The reference also talks about LTO for specific use cases, so another criterion could be if the response mentions LTO. The samples also discuss sodium-ion batteries as an emerging alternative, so that's another point.\n\nAdditionally, the reference and samples compare different battery types in terms of energy density, cycle life, and temperature performance. So criteria could be about whether the response addresses these factors. Also, the importance of supply chain stability and cost-effectiveness.\n\nWait, the user wants 8 criteria. Let me list possible ones:\n\n1. Does the response identify LFP as the primary preferred battery type for cost and performance?\n2. Does the response mention the cost advantage of LFP compared to other types?\n3. Does the response highlight the safety and thermal stability of LFP?\n4. Does the response compare LFP with NMC/NCA in terms of performance trade-offs?\n5. Does the response mention LTO as an alternative for specific applications?\n6. Does the response discuss sodium-ion batteries as a potential alternative?\n7. Does the response address the energy density and cycle life of different battery types?\n8. Does the response consider supply chain stability and cost-effectiveness in the selection?\n\nI need to make sure each criterion is binary and specific. Let me check if these are covered in the reference and samples. The reference does mention LFP as the main choice, NMC/NCA for high performance, LTO for specific uses, sodium-ion as an emerging option, and factors like cost, safety, energy density, cycle life, and supply chain. So these 8 criteria should cover the key points. Now, I need to translate these into Korean, assign importance and weight, and ensure they are binary.\n</think>\n\n{\n  \"criteria\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R1\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.5,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 리튬인산철(LFP)을 가격과 성능 균형에서 가장 선호하는 배터리로 명시합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R2\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.3,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 LFP가 코발트·니켈 프리로 원가 안정성과 열안정성 장점을 설명합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R3\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 NMC/NCA를 고에너지 밀도와 장거리 성능 요구 시 대안으로 제시합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R4\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 LTO를 극저온·초장수명 특수용도에서 사용할 수 있음을 언급합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R5\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 나트륨이온을 저가·자원 분산 전략으로 검토할 수 있음을 제시합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R6\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 에너지 밀도, 수명, 저온 성능 등 성능 지표를 비교 분석합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R7\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 공급망 리스크와 TCO(총소유비용)를 기업 선호 요인으로 설명합니다.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"R8\",\n      \"axis\": \"instruction_following\",\n      \"importance\": \"essential\",\n      \"weight\": 0.2,\n      \"polarity\": \"positive\",\n      \"text_ko\": \"응답은 용도별 선택 가이드(예: ESS, EV, 산업용)를 구체적으로 제시합니다.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}
